title: The Third Charm
synopsis: Joon-Young is a 20-year-old university student. He is a neat, good student, wearing unassuming glasses, jeans, white socks and white sneakers. He doesn't care about fashion. Joon-Young plans more than necessary and he is sensitive. Joon-Young then takes part in his first blind date. There, Joon-Young meets Young-Jae and they begin to date. Young-Jae, is also 20-years-old, is emotional, spontaneous and honest. She doesn't have parents, but she is really close to her older brother. They live together and rely on each other. Her dream is to become rich and she decided to work as a hairdresser's assistant rather than going to a university. A friend then dragged her to a blind meeting with a university student. There, she meets Joon-Young who has a totally different personality from her. A romantic comedy that follows the realistic romance of two individuals with completely opposite personalities who unexpectedly met on a group blind date.

title: Criminal Justice
synopsis: Ever wonder what it’s like to be a criminal? Wonder no more! ‘Criminal Justice’ takes us on a journey through the justice system. Series 1 features Ben Coulter, a young man accused of murder after a drunken and drug-filled night out. He can’t remember any of it but there’s blood on his hands. Series 2 follows troubled housewife Juliet after she’s stabbed her abusive husband in their very own bed.

title: 18if
synopsis: This anime is an adaptation of a smartphone puzzle RPG [18:A puzzle that connects to you]. The story is set in a modern world where an odd and strange disease called Sleeping Beauty Symptom is rapidly invading through. The player, called as "divers", is requested to access to the dreamland to save patients by breaking the shackles of their own hearts, and sending them back to the real world.

title: My First Love
synopsis: Kang Shin-Woo is a math teacher with a good looking appearance. He has not forgotten his first love Han Ji-Soo for the past 10 years. By an accident, he travels to the past when he was a high school student. There, he meets his younger self. Kang Shin-Woo struggles to make the younger Kang Shin-Woo's love come true.

title: Organic Love
synopsis: Hanbyul wants to become a famous actor, but she goes into Farming University because her family can’t afford other college registration fee. Ju-seouk was a promising tennis player, after his brother's death, he gets into Farming University to take the family business. Joo-jin believes that farming could be smarter, and wants to develop the smart-farming system. Han-byul  and Ju-seouk fall in love with each other. They have different dreams, but they grow up at the university and learn how meaningful farming is.

title: The World Of The Married
synopsis: Ji Sun-woo, a family doctor who seemingly lives a perfect life, starts to seek revenge on her husband Lee Tae-O, whom she suspects is having an affair.

title: Rental Magica
synopsis: Due to his father's disappearance, Itsuki Iba has to take over the family business: a magician dispatch service called "Astral". Astral basically employ countless magicians and other supernatural beings in order to send them out to help those who need magical assistance. As a leader, Itsuki now has to be tough, commanding, and reliable, but there's one problem: he's a coward. Also, in order to run a successful business, he has to connect with his employees, which is more difficult than it seems due to his personality and lack of magical ability. But not only does he have to deal with his own employees, he also has to deal with those who threaten the family business.

title: ID : Gangnam Beauty
synopsis: Mirae undergoes plastic surgery, hoping it will change her life. But it backfires when she remains unnoticed by the one she loves.

title: White Collar Boxing
synopsis: White Collar Boxing League is an exciting opportunity for people with no boxing background to experience the exhilarating sport of boxing.

title: Roadtrip In Malaysia Special
synopsis: This was our first time of all, exciting road trips to recommended places in Malaysia.

title: Relationship 101 with Kyung-Seok and Mi-Rae
synopsis: Here's some love and relationship tips with Kyung-Seok (Cha Eun-Woo) and Mi-Rae (Lim Soo-Hyang) from 'Gangnam Beauty'.

title: Love Won't Wait
synopsis:
Wan Shicheng had a humble beginning from a street food stall, working his way up and eventually opened the largest restaurant in town, the "Prosperous Family", after forty years of hard work. However, at the height of his career, he faces serious troubles at home.

His eldest daughter, Wan Jialing (played by Cecilia Cheung), lost her son three years prior, and has since been getting cold shoulders from his husband Song Qiaozhi (played by Vanness Wu) and getting bullied by her mother-in-law Zhang Yizhen. His daughter-in-law Zheng Qingtian has been selflessly committed to taking care of the family and the restaurant, yet her husband, Sicheng's eldest son Wan Jiale, betrayed her. Sicheng's youngest daughter Wan Jiani has no plan to get married, yet had a one night stand with rich guy Lee Zimin and got pregnant. Shicheng's wife Chen Shuying was upset with the selfish way Shicheng deal with his children and decided to run away from home.

These challenges forced the Wans to grow, they've learned to reflect on their past mistakes and appreciate what they have now. In the end, they helped each other to get through these challenges and achieve a happy ending together.

title: Girls Dorm's Secrets
synopsis:
Freshman Yi-Shuan is very excited to leave home and move to her college dorm. Strangely, due to the female pheromone in the house, Yi-Shuan and her other two roommates all have their periods on the same night, which is the synchronization of the menstrual cycle, also called: McClintock effect. Moreover, because of this effect, Yi-Shuan and her roommates start to see a ghost named: Chun-Qio. Chun-Qio is a virgin ghost, who is a believer of pure romance. On the other hand, the first roommate: Jessica is a party slut, who loves to party and selfie. And, the second roommate: Li-Chi is a chubby girl, who turns everything into fate and Tarot cards.
How will these 3 girls with such different personalities, who share the same period date, spend their dorm life together? Moreover, can these 3 cute-and-smart girls help Chun-Qio lose her virginity so that she can move on to be more of herself, even as a ghost? The craziest comedy about girls’ dorm life that you have ever seen!

title: Dendang Cinta Wulan
synopsis: Wulandari adalah gadis desa yang bermimpi menjadi penyanyi dangdut terkenal.  Suatu hari ayahnya sakit dan dia terpaksa meminjam uang ke Barja, seorang lintah darat, untuk biaya pengobatan. Barja mengambil kesempatan ini untuk mendekati Wulan. Ingin lepas dari lilitan Barja, Wulan memutuskan untuk menjadi penyanyi dangdut agar bisa membayar hutangnya. Sebuah profesi yang sangat ditentang sang ayah.

title: Gober
synopsis: Drama komedi mengenai perjuangan hidup para driver ojek online berbasis aplikasi yang disebut Gober. Kemunculan pertama aplikasi ojek online ini hadir di serial Tukang Ojek Pengkolan. Gober mengisahkan petualangan Beben, bukan hanya memperjuangkan keinginan dan kepuasan pelanggan, tapi juga memenangkan hati Karina dan orang tuanya yang cenderung tidak setuju dengan profesi Beben sebagai driver ojek online.

title: Aku Bukan Ustadz Reborn
synopsis: Nabila pergi ke Kairo untuk kuliah sedangkan Soleh tetap melanjutkan hidupnya. Ia bersama teman-temannya membentuk komunitas majelis roda dua. Komunitas geng motor yang punya misi menebar kebaikan. Seiring perjalanan hidupnya yang baru, Soleh bertemu dengan dua wanita. Rianti, Dokter muda yang kini praktek di kampungnya, kampung Cibuaya, dan juga Alya, seorang anak geng motor. Kisah Soleh bersama dua wanita baru dalam hidupnya baru saja dimulai.

title: Tin Star
synopsis: The epic thriller starring Tim Roth returns for its second series, as Anna offers her father a chance at forgiveness when she tasks him with saving Pastor Johan Nickel, the head of a family who have taken her in, from destruction.

title: Aku Gak Takut
synopsis: Mereka adalah lima sekawan yang gemar mendengar cerita-cerita misteri. Setiap kali berkumpul, mereka selalu berceritakan akan hal-hal yang berbau mistis, seram, atau menegangkan

title: Beauty in the Closet
synopsis: The current emperor at the time neglects his duties and spends time playing and frolicking with the ladies. He also has a habit of hunting foxes late at night. With their declining population and innocent deaths rising, the enraged Fox Clan wages a war against the royal family. They reserve a special pearl that boosts power and beauty to the consumer, which is stolen by the pair of sisters and split between them. They enter the Palace as dancers to fulfill the mission of killing the Emperor. But before the sisters could kill the emperor, he’s abruptly assassinated, and the throne goes to his brother.

title: Always a Boy Friend, Never a Boyfriend Season 1: Can You Love Your Coworker
synopsis: A romantic drama about an ambiguous romantic relationship between two coworkers.

title: Bride Of The Century
synopsis: Doo-Rim is a poor orphan girl who lives on a small island and looks after her grandmother. She works hard to save up for her grandmother’s operation costs. One day, she is presented with an irresistible offer from a rich family - she is to pretend to be their missing daughter, Yi-Gyeong, and all her grandmother’s medical bills would be covered in return. As she begins to be trained intensively to fill the shoes of Yi-Gyeong, she falls in love with Gang-Ju (Lee Hong-Ki), who is Yi-Gyeong’s fiancé and the successor to TaeYang Corporation. Unfortunately, a century-year-old curse runs through the TaeYang family – the first son’s bride always dies. Will Doo-Rim beat the curse and prevail?

title: Misty
synopsis: Hye-Ran stands accused for the murder of her former lover. Her husband is pulled in to defend her, despite her cheating on him.

title: When The Weather Is Fine
synopsis: After a series of unfortunate events, Mok Hae-won (Park Min-young) quits her job in Seoul and goes back to Bookhyun Village, in Gangwon Province, where she briefly lived when she was in high school. There, she meets again her former classmate and neighbor, Im Eun-seob (Seo Kang-joon). He also came back to Bookhyun after leaving the village for a few years and now owns a bookstore.

title: Relationship 101 with Joon-Young and Young-Jae
synopsis: Here's some love and relationship tips with Joon-Young (Seo Kang-Joon) and Young-Jae (Esom) from 'The Third Charm'.

title: Mythical Myanmar Bagan
synopsis: Two famous models from Myanmar - May Toe Khine and Naw Phaw Eh Htar travel across exotic ancient city of Myanmar, Bagan to discover culture, heritage and beauty.

title: Best Of World Of Buzz
synopsis: Bringing you the best of World Of Buzz.

title: Copper
synopsis: Set in the Five Points neighborhood of New York City in the 1860s, focusing on a rugged young Irish cop who is forced to navigate his unruly and dangerous immigrant neighborhood while interacting with the uptown Manhattan crowd and the black community.

title: The Politician’s Husband
synopsis: The Politician’s Husband is a political drama, a bookend to Paula Milne’s phenomenally successful Emmy and Bafta winning mini serial The Politician’s Wife.

title: Hamada's Holiday In Hawaii
synopsis: The popular ""Hamada's Holiday in..."" series, where the legendary comedy duo Downtown's Masatoshi Hamada travels to various places with his ""kohai"" or ""junior"" comedian friends. This time, the guys head to the eternal paradise, Hawaii. However, this time, the clichéd Waikiki is off limits! The theme is ""hidden gems of Hawaii."" Like the other trips, the ""kohai"" guys propose travel plans as well as post photos on the official Instagram account, as they proceed with the trip.

title: Catatan Harian Aisha
synopsis: Aisha gadis sholeha yang berada di tengah kehidupan remaja kota penuh hedonisme. Siswi pindahan Sukabumi ini tampil mencolok dengan penampilannya yang berbeda 180 derajat dari teman-teman di sekolah barunya. Kehadirannya menarik perhatian siswa lain, termasuk Raffi. Kesan pertama yang buruk diantara keduanya menjadi awal dari kisah panjang Aisha di lingkungan yang baru.

title: Good Behavior
synopsis: Based on the Letty Dobesh books by Blake Crouch, the seductive thriller "Good Behavior" centers on con artist Letty Raines and her inability -- despite good intentions -- to consistently live a clean life. Fresh out of prison, Letty attempts to reunite with her 10-year-old son and keep in regular contact with her parole officer, whose motives for helping her are questionable. But after she overhears a hit man being hired to kill a man's wife, Letty sets out to derail the job and finds herself on a collision course with the killer, entangling herself in a dangerous and seductive relationship.

title: Always a Boy Friend, Never a Boyfriend Season 3: The Ex and the Fling
synopsis: A romantic drama about an ambiguous relationship between two friends.

title: Mercurio's Menu
synopsis:
This colourful and quirky series mixes two great lifestyle passions – travel and food – with the affable Paul Mercurio as tour guide and cook.
Viewers join Paul on a culinary adventure, discovering Australia’s wonderfully fresh produce and cuisines in magnificent destinations.
Each episode sees Paul visiting regional Australia to meet a local chef. This chef acts as tour guide, introducing Paul to produce markets, farms, wineries and breweries.
After a day inspired by local seasonal food, they create dishes that capture the essence of the area.

title: The Lost Tomb
synopsis: This drama is adaption of Kennedy Xu's novel series"Grave Robbers’ Chronicles". 50 years ago, a group of Changsha grave robbers dug out manuscripts of the location of treasures from Warring states, but an encounter with an undead rendered almost the whole group dead. In the present, the young grandchild of the sole survivor, Wu Xie, discovers a secret within his grandfather's notes. Together with his third uncle, Wu Sansheng, and a few other experienced tomb robbers, to search for the treasure. But what no one expected to find the intriguing mysteries that accompanied their tomb robbing adventure - just who was the owner of that tomb? Will they be able to find the real coffin? And just where will these puzzle lead the group?

title: Yokkao
synopsis: Premium Muay Thai gear handmade in Thailand YOKKAO events are recognized as biggest Muay Thai events in the world. In September 2013, YOKKAO announced the signing of a partnership with UK SuperShowDown promoter, to promote YOKKAO fight events in England. The partnership started formally with YOKKAO 8 on 8 March 2014, at the Macron Stadium in Bolton, UK. The stadium has since become one of a regular venue for YOKKAO events in the UK.

title: Premier League: A Whole New Ballgame
synopsis: A look at the intrigues and the machinations behind the creation of what is now the world's most watched and valuable football league.

title: Kisah Tanah Jawa: Merapi
synopsis: When a friend goes missing and is presumed dead after hiking Mount Merapi. Andi & Baboon mounts an ill-fated expedition to find the truth. They are unprepared for what lies in wait.

title: iflix Quizzles: Beauty Inside
synopsis: Let's see how well you know the complicated journey of two individuals struggling with the bizarre conditions they have in the Korean series 'Beauty Inside'.

title: Dewi
synopsis: Kisah bermula ketika Dewi baru saja ditinggal oleh suaminya Bayu yang meninggal dunia karena kecelakaan. Setelah kepergian Bayu, ia terkejut bahwa suaminya ternyata memiliki anak yang bernama Abi dari wanita lain. Sebelum meninggal, Bayu berpesan kepada Dewi untuk merawat anaknya itu.

title: iflix Quizzles: The Third Charm
synopsis: Two individuals, two completely opposite personalities. Let's see how well you know Joonyoung and Youngjae in the Korean series 'The Third Charm'.

title: Black Ops
synopsis: "Black Ops" brings viewers along on top-secret special operation missions. The series reveals how elite military units in different countries carry out high-risk/zero-recognition assignments. Expert testimony and dramatic re-enactments tell the inside story on each operation, including the battle against the Taj Palace terrorists in Mumbai, the hunt for Abu Musab al-Zarqawi, the killing of Osama bin Laden, the SAS raid in Sierra Leone, the Moscow theater siege, and the Lufthansa hostage rescue in Mogadishu.

title: The Good Place
synopsis: Michael Schur’s hit afterlife comedy "The Good Place" enters its fourth and final season, with returning fan-favorites Eleanor (Kristen Bell), Michael (Ted Danson, Emmy® nominee for Outstanding Lead Actor in a Comedy Series), Chidi (William Jackson Harper), Tahani (Jameela Jamil), Jason (Manny Jacinto) and Janet (D’Arcy Carden). Having earned one last chance to get into the Good Place, the Soul Squad must prove their worthiness by helping four newcomers, specifically chosen by The Bad Place to drive them crazy, become better people. Will the gang find moral redemption or does eternal torment await? The journey promises to be as hilarious and unexpected as ever.

title: Jon Atherton: Disoriental (Uncensored)
synopsis: “Disoriental”:  comedic misadventures in the Orient told through the life story of one unique Asian: A white one.

title: Mini Recipes
synopsis: Learn how to cook lovely short recipes in 2 minutes!

title: Men On A Mission
synopsis: It is a sitcom talk show program set in a school. In each episode, new celebrity guests appear as transfer students at the 'Brother School' where seven mischievous brother students wait for them. The show consists of several dynamic sessions. In ‘Guess About Me,’ Celebrity guests create random, secret questions about themselves. Then the hosts called 'Knowledgeable Bros' make humorous guesses to get the answers. Another session is ‘Bros Inside’ an ad-lib skit show, where entertainers are given only the setting for a story and have to perform completely ad-libbed skits. In this new unique format, it is impossible to predict what will happen each week!

title: Office Watch
synopsis: Manager Lee joins the office and threatens everyone for different reasons. As a result, the employees, who despise each other, decide to build an alliance.

title: The Destiny Of White Snake
synopsis: Inspired by a legendary folk tale, The Destiny of White Snake tells a heart-wrenching love story between an immortal and a human. She is Bai Yao Yao, a white snake roaming the mortal realm when she meets Xu Xuan, the master of the medicinal valley. There is a also second couple pairing between Xiao Qing, a green snake whose fate becomes intertwined with a demon catcher named Qi Xiao.

title: UnREAL
synopsis: UnREAL gives you a very real look at what goes on behind the scenes of reality shows. It centres around the production team of a “The Bachelor”-style dating show called “Everlasting” --  mainly the producer, Rachel Goldberg and her boss, Quinn King. Quinn constantly pushes Rachel to swallow her integrity and do anything it takes to drum up salacious show content to rebuild the show after an epic meltdown the season before. How does Rachel do this? She turns into a manipulative b*tch who stops at nothing just to create drama of massive proportions. Money, sex, power. Right?

title: Melo Suits Me
synopsis: They rocked their youth & thought everything was great. But they soon realise that life in the 30s is a whole new roller coaster ride.

title: Night of the Fight: Hatton's Last Stand
synopsis: ‘Night of the Fight’ is an unprecedented, behind the scenes account of events leading up to, during and after five time World Champion Boxer Ricky Hatton’s comeback fight at the MEN arena, Manchester in 2012.

title: Six
synopsis: When Navy SEAL Team Six is sent on a mission to Afghanistan to eliminate a terrorist leader, everything goes haywire when they discover that an American citizen is working with the bad guys.

title: The People's Queen
synopsis: What happens when you bring 5 pageant hopefuls to live in a mansion for 6 weeks with 2 over-the-top pageant coaches? While we all know it takes a village to create a beauty queen, Cece Asuncion and Voltaire Tayag set out to shape The People’s Queen!

title: All Out!
synopsis: In rugby, there is no ace striker, there is no number four batter, so who is the star of the team? The story begins at school entrance ceremony of Kanagawa High School where Kenji Gion, a small but gutsy go-getter joins the rugby club.

title: Broken Promises
synopsis: Broken Promises tells the story of Ana, Frida and Seleni, three beautiful young girls who are tricked with the promise of getting their dream life. They’ve never seen each other but they will become friends, forced into it when they meet at a point of no return and live the worse nightmare a woman can have: to be a victim of Human Trafficking.

title: Preman Pensiun
synopsis: Setelah kematian istrinya, ia menyatakan pensiun menjadi preman. Pernyataan hanya disampaikan kepada tangan kanannya, Muslihat. Alasan ia pensiun dikarenakan sebelum istrinya meninggal, istrinya berujar akan menunggunya di surga. Bahar berpikir, bahwa kalau dia terus menjadi preman, tidak mungkin akan sampai ke sana.

title: Clean with Passion for Now
synopsis: Jang Seon-gyeol is obsessed with hygiene and tidiness. But what happens when the girl he falls in love with, is the total opposite?

title: Space Battleship Tiramisu
synopsis: Being the top driver of the battleship, who succeeded in defeating the enemy attack, protecting the security of the battleship and defending the peace of the earth. This series is telling about the daily funny stories happened around the main character in the universe. Moreover, each character, the battleship, and the perfect painting of the aircraft have also become a big selling point.

title: Shark Shooters
synopsis: From the prehistoric seven-gill, to the incomparable great white, Scubazoo’s underwater cameramen and photographers have travelled the world photographing sharks. Join colleagues and great friends Jason Isley and Roger Munns as they attempt to gain dazzling imagery of these misunderstood predators.

title: Volkswagen Ameo Cup 2018
synopsis: As India’s only one-make-championship motorsport race, the series follows the journey of 20 drivers across 5 months and 3 cities as they compete for the top honors. This series aims to encourage motorsport among the masses by showcasing exclusive and behind-the-scene footage of rigorous training, fitness and race sessions.

title: Strong Woman Do Bong-Soon
synopsis: She is no ordinary woman. Do Bong Soon is a woman who possesses Herculean strength. She can crush objects in her bare hands when she holds them too tightly. Although Bong Soon longs to be a dainty, elegant woman that men fall in love with, she can’t deny her superhuman strength. Her special attribute allows her to get a job as a bodyguard for Ahn Min Hyuk, the chaebol heir with eccentric tendencies who runs a gaming company. Bong Soon’s childhood friend In Gook Doo has had a secret crush on her since elementary school. How will he react when sparks begin to fly between Bong Soon and her crazy boss?

title: GOT7 Golden Key
synopsis: Golden Key' is a 2-way communication program with the fans. We can see how GOT7 Mark and Youngjae express their thankful feelings to their fans.

title: Indonesia From Below
synopsis: Home to more than 17,000 islands and 85% of the world’s coral species, Indonesia is regarded as the world’s best diving destination.

title: Siluman Ular
synopsis: Sebuah kerajaan di negeri Ular, yg dipimpin oleh Ratu Siluman Ular, Risma. Risma memiliki seorang anak perempuan Sinta yang berusia 6tahun dan telur yang belum menetas. Risma memiliki Mustika Sion yang sangat sakti dan diincar oleh orang banyak. Kerajaan Siluman di serang oleh Naagraj. Dia adalah Pawang Ular dan Dia bersama Rendra.

title: Anak Jalanan
synopsis: Boy adalah seorang remaja berpenampilan urakan dan cuek tetapi juga saleh dan tampan. Gaya Boy yang keren dan gagah saat mengendarai motor dan sering memenangkan balapan, membuat ia digilai gadis-gadis seusianya. Sikapnya yang penuh kharisma khas anak muda, membuatnya ditunjuk sebagai ketua perkumpulan anak motor Warrior. Tidak hanya di area balap, di sekolah pun Boy menjadi idola. Sikapnya yang ramah, cuek tetapi pintar dan atletis, membuatnya selalu menjadi pusat perhatian.

title: The Magicians
synopsis: Based on Lev Grossman’s best-selling book series, "The Magicians" follows Quentin Coldwater, a highly intelligent but socially withdrawn twenty-something secretly obsessed with a series of fantasy novels he read as a child about a magical land called Fillory. Beyond that, Quentin's life is dull until he finds himself admitted to a very secret, exclusive college of magic in Upstate New York, where he receives a thorough and rigorous education in the practice of modern sorcery. However, magic doesn’t bring the happiness, adventure, and meaning that he thought it would…until he and his friends discover that Fillory is real.

title: Magic Hour The Series
synopsis: Magic Hour The Series is a continuation of Raina and Rangga’s love story. While Raina is set to spend the rest of her life with Rangga, her love is challenged by Rangga's own secret wish. How will this entanglement of hearts and complication of feelings that span between Jakarta, New York and Bali be sorted out? Will Raina eventually find one more magic hour in her life?

title: When We Were Young
synopsis: Chu Yin Yin is a proud and intelligent girl who always keeps ahead of others, combining beauty and wealth. It may be said that she is the winner of life. Xia Er is an internet star who grew up in a small village. She used to sell clothes, cosmetics, and unreal stories online for a living. No one knows that these two girls were adopted by different families separately in their childhood. In an accident, their identities were  swapped. Xia Er replaced Chu Yin Yin although she can’t adapt to a luxurious life. Chu Yin Yin lost her memories, she went to the third-tier school in the village. Both of them try to find out solutions, but every time they ended up in danger. Before the truth is revealed, Xia Er suddenly finds a hidden secret: her sister's falling into the river was not an accident! Suicide or murder? In the confusing suspense, the mystery will be solved.

title: Oi Jaga Lambe 2
synopsis: With the rising tension in society, 4 indonesian comic takes the stage and bring up the comedy from their own personal experience with sex, religion, and the powers that be!

title: Roman Picisan The Series
synopsis: Roman Picisan mengisahkan tentang Roman (Arbani Yasiz) yang jago membuat puisi. Teman-temannya kerap memanggilnya Rompis lantaran hobi membuat puisi gombal. Tak hanya jago soal puisi, Roman juga jago soal menaklukkan hati wanita karena parasnya yang tampan dan kebaikan hatinya. Hingga pada suatu hari, SMA 712 tempat Roman bersekolah kedatangan murid baru yaitu Wulandari (Adinda Azani).

title: Kun Anta
synopsis: Kisah anak muda yang masih berada di pesantren Kun Anta bernama Haikal tak menduga jika sepupunya yang juga seorang anak muda berumur 17 tahun bernama Elang juga masuk ke pesantren tempat Haikal menimbah ilmu selama ini.

title: What's Wrong with Secretary Kim
synopsis: What's Wrong with Secretary Kim is a romantic comedy that focuses on the relationship between Lee Young Joon and Kim Mi So. Lee Young Joon is the narcissistic vice president of a company who has it all, while Kim Mi So is his secretary known for her competence.

title: Sleepless In Love
synopsis: A couple of guys and girls spend their sleepless nights thinking about romantic dilemmas.

title: Britannia
synopsis: An epic drama set in 43AD as the Roman Imperial Army – determined and terrified in equal measure - returns to crush the Celtic heart of Britannia - a mysterious land ruled by warrior women and powerful druids who can channel the powerful forces of the underworld. Or so they say.

title: The Package
synopsis: Dumped & stranded in Paris, Soso is forced to work as a tour guide. Life gets worse when she’s assigned a group of eccentric tourists.

title: Weird Underwater World
synopsis: The ocean: it’s a weird and wonderful place, bursting with bizarre, brilliant and beautiful life. Like the dinky but deadly blue-ringed octopus, unequivocally ugly stargazer, freakish frogfish, or even the largest animal to have ever graced the planet.

title: Sketch
synopsis:
A secret team operated by the National Police Agency solves cases by utilizing the skills of Yoo Shi-hyeon, someone who draws pictures of the future in order to express what she predicts.
Detective Kang Dong-su comes across Si-hyeon’s sketch predicting his fiancée Min Ji-su’s death, and saves her from a life-threatening situation.
An innocent woman gets sacrificed in the process, and the team which was going after the notorious killer ‘Huigwangi’ encounters an even larger presence which is pulling the strings.

title: Next Of Kin
synopsis: GP Mona Harcourt's life is torn apart when her brother is abducted and her nephew falls under suspicion of complicity in the crime.

title: Cooking California Style
synopsis: Join Jack Smiler and Max Bobritsky as they show you how to cook California Style

starring.actor: Hosts Jack Smiler and Max Bobritsky

title: Stand Up Comedy Indonesia
synopsis: Watch all kinds of humour be it appropriate on inappropriate be thrown across the halls of the Stand Up Comedy show by your favorite Indonesian comedians

title: Pagan Peak
synopsis: When a gruesomely staged body is found, propped up on a mountain pass in the Alps close to the German-Austrian border, two detectives are sent to investigate. For German detective Ellie, this is the first real challenge of her career; her Austrian counterpart Gedeon though seems to have lost any ambitions in his job. Very soon, they discover more crime scenes with symbolically posed victims, reminiscent of pagan rituals. It all seems to be part of a bigger, sinister plan. Ellie finds herself under increasing pressure to understand the deranged killer's motives so she can stop him. The hunt leads them ever deeper in the dark valleys and archaic Alpine customs - and the paranoid world of the killer.

title: Nina Sahabat Sejati
synopsis: Menceritakan tentang kisah seorang gadis kecil bernama Nina yang lucu terbangun dari tidurnya, tak ada siapapun di rumah itu. Pikirnya ibu masih di kantor dan ayah masih di luar kota. Tiba – tiba terdengar kaca jendela pecah. Anak – anak yang melempar bola malah bisik – bisik kalau rumah itu adalah rumah hantu. Kemudian Nina ingin memarahi mereka

title: Libra Of Nil Admirari
synopsis: The main character was born in aristocrat decides to get married in order to save the fallen family. Meanwhile, her younger brother was involved in the events that cause by an ancient book.Through her younger brother’s event, she can detect the “rare things” which emerges other people’s soul and emotion-Aura. And the Imperial Library Intelligence Asset management Bureau is called as “Fukurou. This girl decide to join in Fukurou in order to dig out the truth of of his brother accident.

title: Komplek Pengabdi Istri
synopsis: Di sebuah komplek perumahan, tinggallah berbagai keluarga yang berasal dari suku bangsa yang berbeda-beda. Ada keluarga Komeng, keluarga Jaka, Pak RT, Dibyo, dan masih banyak lagi. Para istri mereka pun berasal dari berbagai suku yang tidak sama dengan mereka.

title: Brainy Bubbly Bug Buddies
synopsis:
Wouldn’t it be great fun for an animated series to focus on the lively workings of the insect world, just as children started exploring the wonders of nature for themselves? Brainy Bubbly Bug Buddies, Fantawild’s new 104-episode series, spins charming tales from the woods to the wetlands, spotlighting a bustling colony of cheerful creepy-crawlies—and the reliable, though sometimes bullying, frog they count as neighbor and friend.

Amid the insect-adventures, audiences will get a bug’s-eye view of the habits and habitats of actual insects of many kinds, and will learn how these creatures thrive in their environments. 

Imagine children everywhere sitting down to be entertained, and getting up with a new understanding of the world around them! 

In Brainy Bubbly Bug Buddies, characters thrive in a lush wetland paradise. Among its inhabitants are Bartle Bee, the fencing-master bumblebee; Flutterby, the elegant butterfly; Strobe and Sparkle, the heart-of-gold firefly brothers; and McBroom, the hardest-working beetle in the land. 

The Marsh is always buzzing with activity, and little viewers will be captivated by the lively blend of action and discovery to be found in its colorful environs. 

Our exoskeletal heroes bring their collective skills and ingenuity to bear on life’s challenges in The Marsh, and in the end, they are rewarded for their efforts. Young learners are thus reminded that problem-solving is often best accomplished as a joint effort—and, coincidentally, that we live in a vast world worthy of exploration at even the most minute level of existence. 

Visits to The Marsh will delight and intrigue, all while nurturing children’s budding quest for knowledge—and imbuing them with a healthy respect for life in the natural realm.

title: Caesar
synopsis: Photographer Alexey Govorkov, Caesar, is a popular blogger. He exposes the police fads. Once he sees the police arrests a serial killer, Artist. Govorkov helps him hide and meets Captain Zvyagin. Caesar is invited to the investigation group. The Moha gives them obvious, but resonant cases. The blogger works for public opinion in favor of the police. Zvyagin suspects that Govorkov is Artist.

title: Mysterious Nurse
synopsis: After her eye transplant, she can see the truth about the death of her doner! She is the only one who can save the Psychiatrist being falsely blamed for Doner’s death. A fantasy mysterious romance between the mysterious nurse and picky Psychiatrist! Would they find the real cause of death and get happy-ending?

title: Mr. Robot
synopsis: Young, anti-social computer programmer Elliot works as a cybersecurity engineer during the day, but at night he is a vigilante hacker. He is recruited by the mysterious leader of an underground group of hackers to join their organization. Elliot's task? Help bring down corporate America, including the company he is paid to protect, which presents him with a moral dilemma. Although he works for a corporation, his personal beliefs make it hard to resist the urge to take down the heads of multinational companies that he believes are running -- and ruining -- the world.

title: Tukang Ojek Pengkolan
synopsis: Di sebuah perkampungan padat di ibukota, tinggalah sepasang suami istri bernama Ojak & Tati. Pernikahan keduanya tidak direstui oleh ibu dari Tati karena Ojak hanya berprofesi sebagai tukang ojek. Bersama dengan dua temannya Pur dan Tisna, Ojak selalu mangkal di pengkolan gang perkampungan mereka. Konflik keseharian rumah tangga Ojak ditambah keseruan kisah para tukang ojek itu mewarnai kehidupan perkampungan padat ini.

title: Riviera
synopsis: This intoxicating thriller follows the moral descent of American art dealer Georgina Clios, whose idyllic life is shattered when her billionaire husband is killed in mysterious circumstances. Riviera’s highly anticipated return picks up in the immediate aftermath of the explosive first series finale, where the Clios family is faced with the tragic death of one of their own. Only this time, the blood is on Georgina's hands.

title: Villa Nabila
synopsis: This film is made based on the real stories that took place at an abandoned house in Johor called Villa Nabila.

title: Genius
synopsis: They are American heroes – legendary icons – luminaries who changed the world through monumental innovations and staggering ingenuity.  They gave us the airplane and the television, MS-DOS and AC / DC, the V-1, the six-gun, the A-bomb and the IPod.  Or at least they take credit for it.  Those fabled inventors were not the only ones behind those fabled inventions. No matter how brilliant they were, the challenges they faced were too big to face alone. But who they were seconded by is a surprise.

title: Confession Couple
synopsis:
This is a drama with a strong message that will remind married
couples who are stuck in a rut what love is like once again!
Almost everyone wishes to return to the moment before they
make the most regrettable decision of their lives. The same goes
for the married couple in this drama, who got married at the
young age of 24 because they were blinded by love. While they
live in regret, they get to be 20 years old all over again. 
The life-changing project for the couple begins.

title: Scratch My Back
synopsis: Having committed various crimes, four young-sters end up doing community service at a luxurious seaside rest home. This is a shock, to them as well as to the residents. It is two worlds colliding. When dark clouds gather above the rest home, only a radical action can avert a disaster. But for that, the senior citizens will have to call upon the four teenagers’ assistance.

title: Wild24: Fierce Felines
synopsis: Felines are known for its ferocious temperament, a trade that makes them one of the most dangerous predators in the wild.

title: Love In Vienna
synopsis: Melody, a production assistant, is instructed to locate and convince pianist Michael Grimaud, who fell off the radar ten years ago, to play at a concert. She finds him in the Austrian Alps where he has retired but things get tricky when sparks fly.

title: Chef Extraordinaire
synopsis: Pieps Chef Extraordinaire invites chefs from around the World to share their secrets.

title: Puberty Medley
synopsis: After transferring schools seven times, Choi Jeongu learns it is easiest not to make friends nor enemies. He sticks to that practice when he transfers into Namil High School, but not for long. The guy sitting next to him, Deokwon, is overly friendly and keeps trying to become friends with him. The class president and the top student of the school, Yang Ayeong, keeps bothering him to do chores for the class. Jeongu succeeds in remaining invisible until one fateful day, when he stands up for Deokwon against a bully, who is constantly picking on him. He mistakenly hits the Brown Bear, Yeokho, and is challenged to a duel. If Jeongu wins, Deokwon will be left alone. When Ayeong tells him to apologize to Yeokho, Jeongu gets angry and blurts out, "Go out with me." A day full of regrets, but Jeongu is not concerned, since he is transferring out in a week anyway… or so he thinks.

title: Girls Can't Fight
synopsis: Instructional grappling moves presented by sexy women of the sport.

title: The Haunted House
synopsis: With help from a 102-year-old goblin dwelling beneath their haunted apartment building, two siblings deal with ghosts and take on spooky mysteries.

title: Spice Islands Of The World
synopsis: Indonesia's Spice Islands: Indonesian Chef Tomy has a fun personality and uses it  to make cooking genuine Indonesian recipes both entertaining and easy. Nothing complicated here just 500 years of Indonesian cooking history and recipes condensed into this introductory educational series. You can actually watch and prepare along with Tomy as he puts together recipes step by step.

title: Rich Man
synopsis: Yoo-chan is a handsome, genius and selfish CEO of the successful IT company. But he has face blindness since he’s abandoned by his mother in his childhood and he is missing his first lover who left him suddenly. One day, a lovely girl like a tomboy, having good memory joins his company and works with him. He feels strangely drawn to her and he slowly changes into a warm-hearted person because of her. They run into each other they open their eyes to love and begin a romance like dark chocolate-slightly bitter but makes you crave for more.

title: Dia Yang Tak Terlihat
synopsis: Nugi pergi melihat lokasi resort yang akan dibuka oleh perusahaan ayahnya, Wirawan. Nugi jatuh cinta pada pandangan pertama dengan Kania. Sejak saat itu, hidup Nugi berubah dan kerap diganggu. Terlebih saat pertemuan keduanya dengan Kania yang menerjunkan dirinya ke jurang. Nugi mencari jasad Kania, tapi tak berhasil. Nugi menemukan anting yang dipakai Kania saat terakhir bertemu. Tanpa Nugi ketahui, Kania selalu mengikutinya kemana pun ia pergi.

title: Ada Dua Cinta
synopsis: Mecca dan Medina adalah dua gadis cantik yang memiliki kehidupan yang sangat bertolak belakang. Mecca dibesarkan oleh Rohim dan Aisyah, sepasang suami istri yang hidupnya serba kekurangan. Namun di keluarga ini hidup Mecca tidak pernah kekurangan cinta dari ayah dan ibunya.

title: Celebrity On Board
synopsis: This Online Music Variety Show is hosted by two famous Taiwan host who are Wing & Biung.  Every episode they will invite famous singer, artiste & Youtuber from Taiwan, China & Malaysia as their guest.  They will play games, chat & sing with the guest in the car.

title: How To Be You
synopsis: How to be You is a travel and lifestyle program that focuses on what's new among men, women in the household, as well as the millennials. While on the road to visit a travel destination, the show features celebrities who have made a profound influence on others. The program also talks about beauty from the inside out. It also advocates health and fitness. In addition, the show raids the kitchen and demonstrates how to whip up gastronomic delights.

title: Deep Fried Masters
synopsis: After deep-fried Oreos, bananas, mozzarella sticks and the latest craze, Churros - what could possibly be next?  These days, inventiveness of deep frying has skyrocketed to another level with fried goods ranging from butter to cola, and even beer!  DEEP FRIED MASTERS features the best frying competitions and a revolving cast of talented judges, each on a mission to prove, once and for all, that everything taste better deep fried.

title: Japallywood Theater
synopsis: Emotional depth delivered by Japanese actors. Amazing scenery made by Japanese landscape. Moving scenes created with Japanese technology. The entire nation of Japan trembled and were moved to tears. Once the audience sees these overwhelming 100% Japanese foreign films with completely original stories, they will surely say, “Japallywood movies are truly the best.

title: Binar Bening Berlian
synopsis: Binar Bening Berlian bercerita tentang kehidupan tiga orang gadis sebaya yang bernama Binar (Celine Evangelista), Bening (Irish Bella), dan Berlian (Asmirandah Zantman). Binar dan Bening merupakan anak kembar dari pasangan Junus (Ari Wibowo) dan Herlina (Yoelitta Palar). Meskipun kembar, Binar memiliki fisik yang lebih sehat dibandingkan Bening. Bening menderita leukemia, yang membuatnya menjadi penghuni rutin rumah sakit di bawah pengawasan dr. Mirza (Christian Sugiono).

title: The Last O.G.
synopsis: This season, Tray goes all in on his dreams of becoming a chef after losing his job. Meanwhile, Shay (Tiffany Haddish) has an intriguing business venture of her own on the horizon.

title: Cold Justice
synopsis: All New Cold Justice follows former prosecutor Kelly Siegler and a team of crime scene investigators and detectives as they crack cold cases.Kelly Siegler, a Texas prosecutor for 21 years who has successfully tried 68 murder cases, and her team of crime scene investigators and trained detectives, put their vast knowledge and experience to work helping local law-enforcement officers and families of violent-crime victims get to the truth.With a fresh set of eyes on old evidence, superior interrogation skills and access to advanced DNA technology and lab testing, Siegler is determined to bring about a legal and emotional resolution. Taking on a different unsolved crime each week, they carefully re-examine evidence, question suspects and witnesses, and chase down leads in order to solve cases that would have otherwise remained cold indefinitely.

title: Rain Or Shine
synopsis: Setelah kehilangan ayahnya dalam robohnya sebuah mal yang fatal, Gang Du kehilangan semangat hidup dan melalui hidupnya yang kacau hari demi hari dengan enggan. Suatu malam, dia dipukuli sampai hampir mati oleh sekelompok orang dan dibuang di sebuah gang sepi. Tepat sebelum dia menyerah dengan hidupnya, seorang wanita, Moon Su, menghampirinya.

title: Explore With The Note
synopsis: A story revolving around Wu Xie, Zhang Qiling, Wang Bang Zi and Wu San Sheng as they start another thrilling tomb-raiding expedition involving the supernatural.

title: Snow Tower
synopsis:
The Snow Tower is a tower of joy and sorrow, gatherings and farewells. This is a legend surrounding the Shadow Sun Saber and Blood Rose Sword.

In the midst of a turbulent time, Snow Tower remains the beacon of hope. Yet unbeknownst to most, Leader of Snow Tower Xiao Shi Shui is gravely ill, and the tower has challenges of their own. At this critical time, the Moon Sect assaulted Snow Tower and dealt a heavy blow to them. With his last dying breath, Shi Shui pass the burden of maintaining peace and upholding justice to his son, Xiao Yi Qing. Under the leadership of Yi Qing, they fight for justice and peace.

Shu Jing Rong was assaulted by the Moon Sect at the Sand Valley, and it costs her dearly. She shed her innocence and face challenges with Blood Rose Sword in her hand, carving out her own legend.

title: Just Go: China
synopsis: Faced with 9.6 million square kilometres, 1.3 billion people and 3,000 years of history, it’s hard to know where to begin your trip to China. This Just Go China special promises to bring you all the affordable highlights the dragon country has to offer. As well as the historic temples and ultra-modern architecture that unite China’s past with its future, Rhys’s quest for adventure will lead him to ancient water cities, mountain cableways, cultural festivals, bustling night markets and some of the most breathtaking scenery in the world.

title: Flower Crew : Joseon Marriage Agency
synopsis: Newly appointed King Lee Soo hires a matchmaking agency to turn the love of his life from a peasant into a queen so he can marry her.

title: At Eighteen
synopsis: Just as Jun Woo thought he had escaped high-school drama, another emerges - a love triangle between him, the popular girl & the bully.

title: Awas Ada Sule Lagi
synopsis: Program situasi komedi yang menyuguhkan cerita terkonsep yang diadaptasi dari kehidupan sehari-hari.

title: Mahar 30 Juz
synopsis: Faris adalah seorang penyanyi band rock yang sedang naik daun dan digemari para remaja. Dia dan anggota bandnya juga memiliki komunitas motor. Faris yang tampan dan vokalis band terkenal tentu saja banyak memikat hati para wanita itu menjadi playboy dan sering kali mempermainkan hati perempuan.

title: Revolutionary Love
synopsis: Rich guy Byun Hyuk (Siwon) and part-timer for life Baek June (Kang Sora), smart elite Jae Hoon (Gong Myung) become friends and tries to revolutionize their lives together.

title: Koombiyo
synopsis: The story revolves around 35 year old bachelor Jehan and his partner in crime Priyantha as they try to exploit the loopholes in the law in order to make a living.

title: Sky Castle
synopsis:
Sky Castle: The name of the luxury private town where wealthy doctors and professors live. It was built by the first president of Joo Nam university, which is the best university in Korea. Most of the residents are doctors and law school professors of the university.

The drama describes all the ins and outs of how the noblewomen make their children enter the top university. It is a comic satirical drama that closely looks behind the scenes at the materialistic desires of the top upper class parents in Korea, who vigorously push forward their plans to make their family a succession of doctors and lawyers, from father to son.

title: Anti Galau Galau Club
synopsis: Jenny, seorang selebgram yang selalu mendapat perhatian dari para cowok. Dua temannya, Brenda dan Nina, mempunyai kanal YouTube yang diikuti banyak penggemar. Brenda seorang vlogger kuliner dan Nina seorang adventure vlogger. Mereka bertiga bersahabat dengan sangat akrab, dan saling melengkapi satu sama lain. Hingga suatu ketika, mereka merencanakan perjalanan ke Bandung. Di situlah berbagai macam konflik mulai bermunculan. Inilah kisah tentang persahabatan, cinta, dan perjuangan menemukan makna dalam hidup.

title: Girl's Power
synopsis: Tears, laughter and dream weave this modern drama series. From different backgrounds, seven women take challenges and overcome harsh training in the same group together. Although various personality, they gradually become good friends. Also, they get over the humps together. This drama aims to use different angles of young adults to inspire audience to pursue their dreams with optimism.

title: Hollywood Makeover
synopsis: Alana Webster reveals the secrets of creating a Hollywood look on a non-Hollywood budget.

title: Will
synopsis: The wild story of young William Shakespeare's arrival onto the punk-rock theater scene in 16th century London -- the seductive, violent world where his raw talent faced rioting audiences, religious fanatics and raucous side-shows. It's a contemporary version of Shakespeare's life, played to a modern soundtrack that exposes all his recklessness, lustful temptations and brilliance.

title: Welcome to Waikiki 1
synopsis: Three very different young men – DONG-GU, the bad luck incarnate who dreams of becoming a film director, JUN-GI, an eccentric actor who performs to make a living, and DU-SIK, a freelancer writer who fiddles around doing nothing most of the time - open a guest house named “Waikiki” in Itaewon where many foreigners come to stay.  Although they have no clue how to run it, they’re eager to earn money to pay for the production of their upcoming film. Joined by Dong-gu’s younger sister SEO-JIN, who actually manages the household in Waikiki; single mother YUN-A, who has made an unexpected landing in the guest house with her mysterious baby; and Dong-gu’s ex-girlfriend SU-A, they all start living together in an uncomfortable and suspicious atmosphere.

title: Half Ton Killer
synopsis: Special follows one of the most controversial and shocking murder mysteries in recent U.S. history. Mayra Rosales, one of the world's heaviest women, confessed to killing her nephew while baby-sitting. But the facts just didn't add up.

title: Menantang Mitos
synopsis: Bercerita tentang lima orang sahabat yang akan berpetualang ke tempat yang punya cerita mistis, mereka berlima akan menelusuri dan mencari tahu mitos yang kian lekat pada tempat tersebut

title: Single Villa
synopsis: Sheng Yu and Ke xin live in a condominium where its residents are forbidden from falling in love, and anyone who violates the rule would be evicted from their apartment. Against all odds, Ke Xin and Xu Lu fall in love with each other and begin an underground relationship.  But the reason why aunt built singel villa is that she wanted to make him marry Man Ni, living together.  Lovely Ke xin and arrogant Sheng Yu, Could they marry each other, despite  Man Ni's distraction?

title: Welcome to Waikiki 2
synopsis: Welcome to Waikiki 2 is a dramedy about the youthful love and passion of the inhabitants of the Waikiki Guest House.  Jun-ki's "evil influence" on his college classmates continues, this time towards his high school classmates.  The crazy plan on the verge of bankrupting the Waikiki Guest House is still on track and antics ensue.  Woo-sik, who used to be a member of a not-sofamous boy-band, falls into Jun-ki's spell and invests every penny he has into the guest house.  Ki-bong, another victim of Jun-ki's sweet talking, used to be a famous baseball player but now he only warms the bench. He makes the wrong decision of investing in Waikiki and now he is about to go broke.  Sooyeon is the first love of all the Waikiki partners but finds herself moving into Waikiki after tragically being stood up at the altar.  Jeong-eun has done every part-time job out there and is a classmate of Jun-ki's film school.  Yuri is Woosik's older sister who becomes the "Queen of Waikiki", as she bends Woo-sik, Jun-ki, and Ki-bong to her will.

title: iflix Quizzles: Strong Woman Do Bong-Soon
synopsis: Let's see how well you know Do Bong-Soon and the people that surrounds her everyday life.

title: Magic Phone
synopsis:
It's a beautiful and fantastic love story like a fairy tale. Poor movie director,  Tae-ji buys a mysterious magic phone and it connects him to the love of his life and popular celebrity, Latte.  Tae-ji meets Latte through the magic phone but every time he uses the magic phone, his eyesight is getting worse so he should get true love before becoming the blind. 
Finally, Taeiji who's almost going blind has to save her in danger.

title: Comedy Boot Camp
synopsis: A serious documentary on comedy that is committed to humor. Struggling rookie comedians learn a unique comedy method from an exceptional trainer for a month. The guest trainer is Kazutoyo Koyabu, who teaches the rookies the essence of the Koyabu Method! Can the trainees complete the task they are assigned and commit themselves to humor?!

title: New Game! (2nd Season)
synopsis: The story follow Suzukaze Aoba, a high school graduate and strong fan of a particular video game, "Fairies Stories". She begins working as a character designer at the previously mentioned game's developer, Eagle Jump. As she works, she becomes acquainted with her co-workers in the character design department, as well as others from the company. For the second season, Sumie Kinoshita is now a chief animation director, while Yuuichi Oka is no longer listed as one. Yuka Itou joins Ishiguro as a color key artist.

title: Paradise Corner
synopsis: Peace and tranquility prevails in an elite suburban settlement “Paradise corner”. Vera, a young girl from Belarus, gets a job as a maid in one of the mansions. However, her real motive is to find her missing friend Olesya, who went here on earnings six months ago. At first, Vera could not believe that someone in this lovely place could hurt her friend. She soon realizes that there is a secret behind the façades of neighboring houses – a secret Olesya might have paid her life for…

title: Injustice
synopsis: On the surface, William Travers is a picture of success -- an accomplished criminal barrister happily living with his wife in a beautiful rural Suffolk home. But scratch beneath that surface and you’ll find that Travers is still recovering from a traumatic series of events that have shaken his belief in the legal system -- should he do what is right, or what is good for his client?

title: Taking New York
synopsis: Taking New York is a constructed reality series that follows the lives and loves of a group of ambitious Brits as they try to make it big Stateside. The cast of cool and inspirational twenty-something's are taking their first steps on the career ladder. Whether they've just arrived to start their new life or already got a foothold in the city that never sleeps, there's never a dull moment in the Big Apple. From working models to the entrepreneur, the art gallery assistant to the event organiser, each are taking on their own careers and doing it their way. The one thing they all share is the desire to succeed. Career highs and lows, new friendships, relationships and break-ups are all laid bare, giving viewers an exclusive insight into what life is like when you are young, hungry for success and living in one of the greatest cities in the world.

title: Oi! Jaga Lambe
synopsis: The sharpest tongues tackling taboos, smashing boundaries and pushing local comedy to a whole new level. Oi! JAGA LAMBE will give the audience a show that’s never been attempted on local TV. What happens when you no longer have to WATCH YOUR MOUTH?

title: Arabia Motors
synopsis: Where Arabian riches and over-the-top lavish lifestyles meets car fanatics.

title: KL Gangster Underworld
synopsis: Shah, pewaris takhta gangster Kg Baru membuat keputusan untuk keluar dari dunia gelap selepas jatuh cinta dengan seorang gadis dari geng saingan. Keadaan menjadi tidak terkawal apabila dia diminta melaksanakan "tugas terakhir" dan secara tidak sengaja mengetahui rahsia yang akan mengubah nasibnya.

title: Knightfall
synopsis: Go deep into the clandestine world of the legendary brotherhood of warrior monks known as The Knights Templar.

title: Hamada's Holiday In Thailand
synopsis: The popular "Hamada's Holiday in..." series, where the legendary comedy duo Downtown's Masatoshi Hamada travels to various places with his "kohai" or "junior" comedian friends. This time, the guys head to Pattaya in Thailand!

title: Beauty Inside
synopsis:
Once a month, a top actress Han Se-gye suffers from a unique type of “magic” that makes her become a different person. At a certain point every month, she has to live one week with a different appearance before coming back to herself. She is known as a troublemaker and has many rumors surrounding her as she occasionally disappears for a week during shoots. However, she is also a star nicknamed “a hundred faces beauty"" because she plays a hundred roles with a hundred faces. Natually this comes with its own set of troubles and issues.

It happened suddenly, but one day, Seo Do-jae could not recognize the faces of anyone in the world. He is otherwise a perfect person in appearance, wealth and ability, but when he meets people, he cannot recognize people without a full memo of their habits, voices, and accessories because of his condition, prosopagnosia.

Seo Do-jae is the only man who can recognize Han Se-gye, who constantly lives in fear of not being remembered. And even with his condition, she is the only woman he can consistently recognize. The only two who can recognize each other.

Healing romance between a woman whose appearance changes to a different person and a man who suffers from an inability to recognize faces.

title: Professional Fighter's League
synopsis: Professional Fighters League (PFL) is the first ever MMA league where individual fighters compete in true sport format of regular season, playoffs and championship. MMA ANALYTICS - PFL also delivers fans the most innovative video experience incorporating fighter data, analytics, social and gaming.

title: Enfusion
synopsis: Enfusion is the pinnacle of Kickboxing where the best fighters build their legacy and face each other for prestigious world titles. The promotion was founded in 2012 and since then, it featured the biggest names in kickboxing.

title: Cosplay Heroes
synopsis: 6 cosplayers, in a premium cosplay competition, undertaking challenges to build cosplay costumes over 9 episodes.

title: Always a Boy Friend, Never a Boyfriend Season 2: Can You Love Your Friend?
synopsis: A romantic drama about an ambiguous relationship between two friends.

title: Jesus Of Nazareth
synopsis: 1977 Beginning before the Nativity and extending through the Crucifixion and Resurrection, this mini-series brings to life all of the sweeping drama in the life of Jesus, as told by the Gospels.

title: Dear Nathan The Series
synopsis: Seorang gadis bernama Salma baru saja pindah SMA. Suatu pagi Salma datang terlambat ke upacara bendera sehingga ia mendapatkan hukuman. Tiba – tiba, ada seorang siswa yang menyelamatkan Salma dari hukuman, ia adalah seorang siswa yang dikenal sebagai murid berandal yang sering tawuran bernama Nathan.

title: Full Metal Panic! Invisible Victory
synopsis: After beating down powerful enemies of Gauron and Gates from the rival organization Amalgam, Jindai High School finally restored the peaceful daily life as usual. However, it didn’t last long……Misbehaved Amalgam officially starts to attack Sousuke Sagara and the others. The 'Mithril' bases of the world have been severely raided! The Merida Island, where Tuatha de Danaan lead by Tessa is sheltering, comes under attack by a large number of missiles and armslaves. Meanwhile, the Devil is also approaching Sousuke and Kaname in Japan! Sousuke, Kaname, Tessa and the others will be facing trials again!

title: New Game!
synopsis: High school graduate Suzukaze Aoba starts her career as a designer in a game production company name [Eagle Jump] where she and her colleagues are appointed to create a new game. Meanwhile, she sets a new goal for herself -- becoming a mature and brilliant lady. This brand new animation is made up of various funny stories in everyday life and will tell about dream, passion and the meaning of being a grown-up.

title: Diary Of A Prosecutor
synopsis: These prosecutors have less power, more paperwork, and all the passion. These prosecutors aren’t your slick, designer-clad prosecutors kicking down high-profile cases with flair. They’re drowning in paperwork and more likely to get kicked than to kick others. Live through the chronicles of these everyday prosecutors who may not lead the most glamorous lives but are second to none when it comes to their belief in justice.

title: Secret Affair
synopsis: Art director Hye-won has fallen for a piano genius. But, she's married and he's in his 20's. Will this relationship end on a high note?

title: Misteri Gunung Merapi
synopsis: Misteri Gunung Merapi adalah sebuah sinetron kolosal yang memunculkan tokoh - tokoh yang sangat populer hingga saat ini, di antaranya adalah Sembara dan Mak Lampir. Kisah ‘Misteri Gunung Merapi’ berawal dari keberhasilan Ki Ageng Prayogo yang membuat Mak Lampir terkurung selama beratus-ratus tahun di goa kaki gunung Merapi.

title: The Lady in Dignity
synopsis: Two women battle to redeem their social status after a twist of fate changes their lives. But to what lengths are they willing to go?

title: AAA Triplemania
synopsis: Triplemanía is the biggest annual professional wrestling event promoted by the Lucha Libre AAA Worldwide (AAA) promotion and is traditionally held in May or June each year, commemorating the anniversary of the foundation of AAA.

title: Jakarta Love Story
synopsis: Aryo, Doni, Teguh, dan Ucok adalah sahabat yang sangat dekat sejak mereka kuliah. Kekompakan mereka tetap berlangsung bahkan sampai mereka sudah berkarier di bidangnya masing-masing saat ini. Aryo mau tidak mau melanjutkan usaha ayahnya dan menjadi yang terkaya di antara mereka.

title: Salah Asuhan
synopsis: Perjalanan cinta Hanafi (Dimas Aditya), perantau dari kota Solok, Sumatra Barat. Hanafi merantau dan melanjutkan pendidikannya di Amerika. Demi mewujudkan impian anaknya, Mariam (Ayu Dyah Pasha) mencari pinjaman uang. Sutan Batuah (Piet Pagau) terpikat dengan kepintaran Hanafi dan memberikan pinjaman uang dengan satu syarat, yaitu menjodohkan Hanafi dengan anaknya, Rapiah (Dinda Surbakti).

title: The Legend Of Dugu
synopsis:
A prophecy bearing the words, """"The World of Dugu: He who has Dugu, has the world"""" reverberates across the lands to imply that the Dugu family was destined to do great things. Because of it, all the attention is turned to Dugu Xin, a court official, and his three daughters, Dugu Ban Ruo , Dugu Man Tuo, and Dugu Jia Luo. Each of the sisters were born blessed with natural beauty and intelligence, and in order to not let the prophecy destroy the sisters' relationship, they all vowed to stick by each other and not let any one of them get hurt. 
However, Dugu Ban Ruo is an ambitious woman and would do anything if it means that the empress' title and throne belonged to her, while Dugu Man Tuo is willing to kill for the greed of wealth and status. Dugu Jia Luo, as the youngest of the sisters, doesn't understand the fight for """"The World of Dugu"""" between her two sisters and tries to live her life in happiness instead of fighting for the crown. But isn't there a saying that the apple doesn't fall far from the tree? A love interest that Jia Luo can't manage to stay away from will also slowly lead her astray into the world where only one Dugu sister can be successful.

title: Dunia Terbalik
synopsis: Dunia Terbalik adalah program series komedi yang mengangkat cerita tentang para suami yang ditinggalkan istrinya untuk bekerja di luar negeri. Dimulai dari kisah Akum, Aceng, Idoy dan satu musuh bebuyutan Aceng, Dadang. Mereka harus mendidik anak serta mengurus urusan rumah tangga yang biasanya menjadi urusan para wanita. Sementara istrinya harus menafkahi keluarga.

title: My Roommate, Miss Ghost Diva
synopsis: “Can you see me?!,,but I’m a ghost,,” A young college student rents a recording-room to become a singer-song writer and the mystery begins. A girl who has been dead for 100 years can’t leave the recording-room because of the curse. “What’s this feeling? Am I in love with a ghost?”. Could a ghost record the songs? What will happen to this young couple. Mysterious first love begins now!

title: Cinta Yang Hilang
synopsis: Diceritakan setahun setelah meninggalnya Mira, Yudha dan Rafi tampaknya kini mulai sama-sama menemukan pilihan hati mereka. Yudha bersama Ilham dan Indah tengah berada di sebuah kapal. Sepertinya mereka hendak pergi ke suatu tempat. Tiba-tiba bocah kecil mengenakan baju berwarna merah muda itu terpeleset dan hampir jatuh

title: Rindu Tanpa Cinta
synopsis: Rindu (Chelsea Olivia) adalah anak dari keluarga biasa sedangkan Rendy (Irwansyah) dari keluarga kaya. Namun, cinta tak membedakan itu hingga mereka berdua akhirnya menikah dan hidup berbahagia. Rendi dan Rindu dikaruniai seorang putri cantik yang bernama Jihan (Chicho Radela). Sayangnya, kisah perjalanan keluarga harmonis mereka berubah ketika Rendy melihat Rindu bersama dengan pria lain.

title: 18 Again
synopsis: Gyung-Hwi is now a hotshot medical resident, having come a long way since his days in high school where he was constantly bullied. But he is suddenly sent back in time, to when he was 18, in order to save his first love.

title: Secret Of The Three Kingdoms
synopsis: The story revolves around the secrets during the Three Kingdoms era, focusing on the intense rivalry between the Imperial Han and Cao Cao rather than the more famous events in history as we know it.

title: Rindu Bilang Sayang
synopsis: Rindu adalah anak dari pemilik orkes dangdut. Anehnya, dia sama sekali tidak menyukai musik dangdut. Ditambah lagi, Sean, teman sekolah yang ditaksirnya adalah seorang anak band. Semakin bertambah alasan Rindu untuk membenci musik dangdut. Hingga suatu hari, sang ayah jatuh sakit dan tidak bisa lagi bermusik. Rindu diminta untuk menggantikan ayahnya demi keberlangsungan orkes dangdut mereka. Masalah lain muncul saat Marsinggi, lintah darat di kampung itu, menagih hutang-hutang keluarga Rindu. Rindu dihadapkan pada pilihan tidak menyenangkan : menikahi Marsinggi agar hutangnya lunas atau menjadi penyanyi dangdut yang dia tidak sukai.

title: Hamada's Holiday In Hokkaido
synopsis: The popular "Hamada's Holiday in..." series, where the legendary comedy duo Downtown's Masatoshi Hamada travels to various places with his "kohai"" or "junior" comedian friends. This time, the guys head to Hokkaido for the first time! The "kohai" guys have looked into the highlights of Hokkaido beforehand and propose travel plans. From the City of Kushiro, Abashiri City, to many other cities... Will the guys be able to satisfy Hamada?

title: Saat Hati Telah Memilih
synopsis: Ini adalah kisah cinta segitiga antara Riri, Haris, dan Andi. Riri memiliki hubungan yang sangat dekat dengan Andi, pria yang mengidap suatu penyakit berbahaya. Riri berharap kehadirannya bisa memberikan semangat kepada Andi. Kedeketan mereka tidak disetujui oleh Iren, Ibu Andi, dan Haris, saudara Andi. Mereka merasa Riri hanya memberikan harapan palsu kepada Andi. Diam-diam Haris juga mencintai Riri. Lalu, hati siapa yang dipilih Riri?

title: UN In Action
synopsis: UN in Action is an award-winning UN video original production of short features series. This monthly series puts a human face on the work of the UN and its agencies around the world. "UN in Action" reports on the work of the United Nations and its Agencies around the world.

title: Jaru Jaru's Shop of Laughs
synopsis: Have you ever laughed so hard that you can hardly breathe? Laugh till you get cramps? Laugh till you cry? It's a great moment that lets you forget all the troubles in life. To make people crack up laughing, the Japanese comedy duo, Jaru Jaru tries to make their targets roll with laughter. Don't miss this ""experimental docu-variety show.

title: Bosch
synopsis: From Michael Connelly’s best-selling novels, comes Harry Bosch -- an LAPD homicide detective with a soft spot for jazz. He’s got more than music on his mind though, the relentless detective pursues the killer of a 13-year-old boy while standing trial on murder charges himself. As the departmental politics heat up, Bosch is set to pursue justice at all costs.

title: Victoria
synopsis:
Queen Victoria, a nineteenth century heroine for our times. Series Two sees the impulsive young queen face the very modern challenge of balancing a growing family with her husband and her work – all while being the ruler of the most powerful nation on earth. 
 
As Victoria’s reign continues into the 1840s, her Kingdom is witness to extraordinary events. Constitutional crises and scandalous romances blossoming at court. The rise of the Chartist movement, the devastating Irish Potato Famine and perilous diplomatic relations that see Victoria travelling to France to try her hand at foreign policy.
 
Victoria and Prince Albert brave each trial on the world stage while also confronting profound personal changes. Facing down loss and betrayal against a dizzying backdrop of their expanding family, royal duties and an adventure to Scotland, they must renegotiate the balance of power in their passionate marriage if they are to thrive as the world’s most influential partnership.

title: Traffic Cops
synopsis: Britain’s longest running and most watched cop show has a brand new home on Channel 5.  Traffic Cops returns to the frontline of our nation’s roads with Yorkshire’s finest.  Over more than a decade Traffic Cops has built a huge and loyal following.  Now, as our Police scale up to combat increasingly sophisticated criminals, Traffic Cops scales up too.  In this series, with the ever-present Jamie Theakston opening each show, we’re with two Yorkshire Forces covering the North and West of the County - from the cities of Leeds and Bradford to the Yorkshire Dales. And the fight against crime is fast and furious.

title: Ms. Hammurabi
synopsis: Every day is a battle for Seoul’s Justice Department. Follow the courtroom drama as the judges try their hardest to get justice served.

title: The Watchers: Beginning
synopsis: The first of a four-part action adventure, four teens fight the rich for justice. Kira’s friend is hit by a car driven by corrupt oligarch, Polyanski. She needs an operation urgently but he refuses to pay the bill. Kira enlists her three friends to help.

title: Queen of Mystery
synopsis: The KBS drama “Queen of Mystery” is a humane mystery series where Serlock, the queen of mystery, and Wanson, a hot-blooded detective, solve the cold cases and help heal the hearts of those whose lives have been affected by crimes. On the surface, Ser-lock seems like an ordinary married woman who wouldn’t have anything to do with solving crimes, but her deductions, which seem sloppy at first but turn out to be brilliant, will make you laugh and cry.

title: Made In Abyss
synopsis: The story follows an orphaned young girl, Riko, who finds and befriends a humanoid robot Reg and descends with it into the titular "Abyss", that leads deep into the Earth, in hopes of finding her mother.

title: Poldark
synopsis: 1783 - Ross Poldark (Aidan Turner) returns to Cornwall to find his father dead, his estate in ruins and his sweetheart, Elizabeth (Heida Reed), engaged to marry his cousin Francis (Kyle Soller). On an impulse, Ross saves street urchin Demelza, (Eleanor Tomlinson), and with her help and a steely resolve, Ross turns around his fortunes despite George Warleggan's (Jack Farthing) best efforts.

title: Borneo From Below
synopsis: A ‘funservation’ series presented by British underwater photographer and dive journalist, Aaron “Bertie” Gekoski. Filmed entirely around the extremely biodiverse island of Borneo, each entertaining and educational episode highlights the unique animals found here and some of the area’s key environmental threats. Throughout Borneo from Below viewers are also provided with tips and techniques to help them improve their photography along the way.

title: Cold Justice: Sex Crimes
synopsis: Devised by Dick Wolf, Emmy-winning television producer who brought the Law & Order franchise to the small screen, Cold Justice comes back for a new series with a focus on sex crimes. The sobering statistics for sex-related crimes in America reveal that there are approximately 240,000 survivors of sexual assault, including men, women and children. Every two minutes, someone is sexually assaulted in the United States. To combat these numbers and bring justice to the survivors of sexual assault, Cold Justice’s investigators Casey Garrett and Alicia O'Neill travel around the country to help local law enforcement solve cases that have sat dormant for years. In this special season of Cold Justice, Casey and Alicia investigate many sex crimes which include the stories of a local grandmother who is brutally attacked in her sleep, of a young girl whose online meeting turned into a real world nightmare, and of a 17-year old unsolved investigation into the rape of a teacher on an elementary school campus.

title: Putri Yang Ditukar
synopsis: Amira (Nikita Willy) dan Zahira (Yasmine Wildblood) memiliki kehidupan yang berbeda. Amira hidup sederhana bersama kedua orang tuanya, Ihsan (Sultan Djorghi) dan Utari (Marini Zumarnis). Sedangkan Zahira hidup mewah bersama kedua orang tuanya, Prabu (Atalarik Syach) dan Aini (Vonny Cornelia), serta ibu tiri Selena (Moudy Wilhelmina) dan kakak tiri Meisya (Citra Kirana).

title: Semua Indah Karena Cinta
synopsis: Aviv dan Bella adalah sepasang sahabat sejak kecil. Aviv tumbuh menjadi pemuda tampan, sabar, tenang, seorang pemimpi. Sosok yang sangat ideal untuk para gadis. Sedangkan Bella lebih emosional, berani membela yang benar, sederhana dan realistis. Beranjak dewasa, Aviv dan Bella saling jatuh cinta. Arta dan Darman, ayah mereka sangat setuju dengan hubungan mereka. Karena sejak dulu mereka bekerjasama membuka perusahaan hingga akhirnya mencapai kesuksesan. Namun Sylvia, Ibu Aviv sangat membenci keluarga Darman. Ia menganggap Darman hanya benalu yang menumpang hidup, karena selama ini Darman hanyalah menyumbang pemikiran saja. Sementara semua modal ditanggung oleh Arta, suaminya.

title: Flint: Redemption
synopsis: After long years of serving in the forces former major Andrey Shamanov tries to live usual life. But when his ex-colleagues need his help even his beloved Nastya can’t make him refuse a dangerous missionto investigate a cause of death of SMU group, who were undergoing drill in the mountains where gang of smugglers were hiding. While working on this case Andrey will face severe trials as the criminals kidnap his beloved and try to blackmail him. Shamanov decides to take the criminals by storm and saves Nastya, releasing several hostages. But the criminals are not going to let Andrey and witnesses leave the secret base…

title: Flint
synopsis: Former soldier Shamanov arrives to a small town to meet his old friend but accidentally finds out that the locals live in fear for their lives. He can’t stand apart and decides to oppose the vicious authorities of the town…

title: Mad Dog
synopsis: Unlike other crime investigation shows thus far, Mad Dog is a KBS crime series that puts the countless forms of insurance fraud in the spotlight. Through the Mad Dog team, the Avengers of the insurance investigation world, viewers will be entertained and shocked by the authentic and novel depiction of the realities of insurance fraud.

title: iflix Quizzles: Rich Man
synopsis: Let's see how well you know the foundation of Next In and the people behind it in the Korean series 'Rich Man'

title: Hafizah
synopsis: Hafizah menceritakan tentang kerelaan seorang wanita yang berbagi hati suaminya. Wanita tersebut adalah Maghda (Fanny Fabriana), seorang dokter kandungan yang harus merelakan rahimnya diangkat karena kanker stadium lanjut.

title: Filosofi Kopi The Movie 2 Ben & Jody
synopsis: Two years after Ben & Jody sold their stall and traveled around Indonesia to share their best coffee, the two best friends stumble upon a deadlock when all of their employees suddenly decided to leave their work. Both were forced to go home and pursue a new dream, making the best coffee shop. With Tarra, as an investor, and Brie, the new barista, they are getting closer to their dreams. However, the presence of these two women also presents a big problem and their friendship is at stake.

title: The Legendary Lackey
synopsis: A legendary transfer student that won a 17:1 fight is here! Tough kid Taeung is the top of the social food chain at his school in Busan! Then shows up the legendary transfer student from Seoul, Chan! And just as peace is restored another new kid from Seoul shows up! It’s Jaeu who went to school with Chan! Why does Chan always seem nervous around Jaeu? And Taeung isn’t happy with the new changes in school!

title: Rock ‘n’ Roll High School
synopsis: A group of rock-music-loving students, with the help of the Ramones, take over their school to combat its newly installed oppressive administration.

title: Bus Driver
synopsis: A high school bus on its way to a retreat blows a tire and stops at the nearest ranch for help. The driver, five troubled students, and their gym teacher find criminals at the ranch who will stop at nothing to make sure their drug operations aren't discovered.

title: My Love For You
synopsis: A father-daughter were living a poor yet contented life. One day, the father received a call from the school and found out that his daughter had been lying about the parents-teacher meeting. Thinking that he had not educated her daughter well, he felt very sorry for his daughter. On the other hand, the daughter knew that her father was actually a blue collar worker instead of a white collor. She did not want to expose his father and being looked down by her peers...

title: Dagger of Kamui
synopsis: An orphan named Taro killed who Tein-Hei told him was the killer of his family. Taro found out, years later that Tein-Hei is the true killer and the man he killed was his father.Taro's revenge attempts start off a trail of assassinations and ninja swords fights spanning from Hokaido, Alaska to California where Tien-Hei's secrets gradually unfold. The revenge road leads to a climactic battle with Tien-Hei on the fall of Japan's Shogun-era.

title: Foul Play
synopsis: Foul Play takes us into the shady world of football match fixing across Asia, where government officials and corporate club owners conspire to ensure that the outcome of the game is determined long before the whistle blows. We follow the story of Simon McMenemy – an English football coach parachuted in to save an Indonesian team after shooting to fame in the Philippines managing their national team. After overcoming his initial culture shock, it becomes clear that the best team doesn’t necessarily win. A sophisticated network of match fixers have an iron grip on the game, players on low salaries are vulnerable to bribes and coaches who raise questions can be removed by team owners.
