Foul Play uncovers, with startling new evidence, a world where international tournaments are set up purely to be fixed, players are given specific instructions on exactly when to take a dive and even when the match isn’t fixed, the referees can ask for a kick back just to ref impartially. As Simon’s frustration grows, it becomes clear that the corruption that is choking Indonesian Football, is the same that is holding back the region across every field.

title: Terlalu Tampan
synopsis: Witing Tresno Jalaran Soko Kulino aka Mas Kulin who is too handsome always avoids entering regular school and chooses to spend almost 100% of his life inside the house. He makes his father, Mr. Archewe, his mother, Bu Suk, and his brother, Mas Okis, worry. They arrange a scenario that succeed in making Mas Kulin agree to spend the last year of his high school years at a special school for boys, Horridson High School. Mas Kulin's handsomeness is then exposed to the outside world so his days go unusual: female teachers faint and he becomes the target of BBM High School students. Including a girl that is too beautiful: Amanda. However, in the midst of all that, Mas Kulin find Kibo and Rere, which make him believe that there are still people who can see him as he is.

title: Mantan Manten
synopsis: As a well-known investment manager, Yasnina has everything. Glamorous life, wealth, and Surya, a fiance who loves her dearly. But the peacefulness of Yasnina's life must end when she is betrayed by Iskandar in a case in her company. In a moment Yasnina's treasure run out of nothing. Not only that, the plan of his marriage to Surya is also at the dangerous tipping point. Ardy, Yasnina's assistant, reminds her that she still has a villa in Tawangmangu which is not confiscated because she has not changed the name's owner. The villa has become Yasnina's only hope to rise again. But to take back the villa, Yasnina had to become an assistant to a traditional bride shaman named Marjanti.

title: We All Cry Differently
synopsis: "I'd rather that my father was dead!" Top student Jihye wants to go on a study abroad program for English. She gets her opportunity but can't make her passport because she's registered under her father whom she has lost contact with. She's always complained about her family but her complaints mount with this issue and she has to learn to listen to her family and sympathize that they're experiencing the same things in different ways.

title: The Ninja: Immovable Heart
synopsis: Reeve, a member of an elite covert group thought not to exist anymore, is captured, beaten and brutally tortured, by the very Governments he used to work for. With the help of his old mentor John Carpenter, Reeve must strip away, and rid himself of the emerging demons of his past, so that he may understand the core essence of Ninjutsu, the Ninja's Immovable heart. He must remember how and why he was captured, and what he is meant to do, before time runs out and his captors discover why he is really here.

title: Remember When
synopsis: Freya menginginkan hidup yang baru, yang lebih seru, yang lebih warna-warni. Freya bosan dengan rutinitasnya yang begitu-begitu saja. Hubungannya bersama Moses yang semula seru, kini terasa begitu menjemukan. Freya ingin seperti Gia dan Adrian, pasangan paling populer di sekolah. Walau masing-masing memiliki pasangan, Freya dan Adrian saling menemukan. Hubungan empat remaja ini menjadi berbeda.

title: Dracula: The Impaler
synopsis: Seven friends begin their Euro-trip at the castle of Vlad the Impaler, the place where he supposedly sold his soul to the devil over 500 years earlier. Their stay at the decrepit castle leads them all into a bloody ritual, a ritual to release Vlad Draculaâ€™s soul from hell.

title: Last Call
synopsis:
Choi Yun Ting was a victim of domestic violence. Her husband was a gambling addict. One day, she suddenly lost her sight when her husband hit her. She met Mak Jan Fai when she called for help at the corridor and she was taken to hospital. Mak later learned that Choi was his crush when they were young. 
Choi was afraid that her husband would hit her again if she recovered. Thus, she refused to attend massage course for the blinds and she refused to accept corneal transplantation. 
After six months, Choi and Mak met each other, Mak collapsed and died while running. God had given him one day to accomplish the last thing in his life and he thought of Choi.

title: Africa’s Outsiders
synopsis: Africa's Outsiders focuses on how animals born with unusual colors (caused by mutations in their genes) have a much harder struggle than animals born with traditional and recognizable colors. This amazing documentary follows the struggle of three extremely different species: a white lion, a white baboon, and a yellow crocodile, though other animals that were born without pigmentation or proper camouflage experience.

title: The Lightest Darkness
synopsis: When a neurotic private eye who struggles to finish the case takes a train voyage to confront the inevitability of his case’s conclusion, his own dark secrets begin to reveal themselves.

title: Bike Boyz
synopsis: Ketika Agus hendak membantu Lilis mencari suaminya yang sudah tiga bulan tidak pulang dan tidak berkabar, Vespanya dicuri orang. Bersama teman-temannya sesama anak Vespa, Agus keliling Bandung mencari Vespanya dan juga suami Lilis. Tanpa sengaja, mereka terlibat dalam kasus yang melibatkan komplotan pencuri, geng motor, teroris, dan polisi.

title: For All Eternity
synopsis: In 1931 in Vienna, Ya Yunlong, a Chinese national studying to be a police officer meets and falls in love with Fanny Ebner.

title: The Eagles Of The Forest
synopsis: “Goooooal!” On the beach, in the streets, over empty fields, far deep down in the jungle: throughout Brazil, everybody plays “Futebol”. But in one particular village, something exceptional is happening… In the heart of the Amazon rainforest, an Indian tribe called the Gavião Kyikatejê (the “Eagles of the Forest”) have formed the first and only native Brazilian professional foot-ball team. Legally registered by the Brazilian Confederation of Football, they won the second division championship, in the state of Para. Now in first division, they have set themselves a new challenge: to make it to the legend-ary Copa do Brasil! Day by day, week after week, we will tell the story of this huge challenge by following several major characters, through training sessions and matches. Meet Zeca, the tribe chief who has had this vision; Aru, the club’s star forward and Gavião’s most sought-after native player; and other passionate members of this ex-traordinary team. The Kyikatejê know the plants and the secrets of the forest and have lived in autarky for centuries, but today they aim to achieve national recognition…

title: Perfection In Imperfection
synopsis: Perfect In Imperfection is based on a true story of a visual artist, Liane Chu. She was looked down by public because of Tourette Syndrome. Nonetheless, she did not give up on persuing her dreams. She learned to channel her creativity into stunning works of art.

title: One Night In Istanbul
synopsis: The adventures of two Liverpool cabbies who want to see their beloved football team play in one of the greatest matches ever - the Champions League Final in Istanbul.

title: Macao Gladiators
synopsis: 35 riders from all over the world meet every year in Macao, the largest motor sports spectacle of Asia, the Macao Grand Prix. Centimeters decide between the perfect track and certain death. Every year drivers crash on the difficult 6.1 km long course. Only in 2012 the Portuguese Luis Carrerra lost his life when his brakes failed and he hit the wall with more than 200 km per hour.  We follow the German Didier Grams together with his Belgian teammate Marc Fissette on the narrow and highly challenging street circuit.

title: KL Gangster
synopsis: KL Gangster tells the story of two brothers Malek (Aaron Aziz) and Jai (Ady Putra) who are entrapped in the gangster world. Malek was imprisoned for years due to being betrayed by his own group's mastermind, Shark (Syamsul Yusof) who is a stepchild of the King (Ridzuan Hashim), a leader of the most influential secret societies in KL. For Malek, after his release from prison, he wants to change the perception of life and stay away from the black life as a gangster.

title: Shopping Street War ～SUCHICO～ From Yoshimoto Shinkigeki
synopsis:
Suchico is a comedy troupe leader. Kasuga is a detective who always gets in trouble. The two team up to solve the mystery of vanishing people. They seemed incompatible, but through interactions with Kasuga’s daughter, Yui, they start to have respect towards one another.
©2016 Yoshimoto Kogyo

They overcome various obstacles and uncover the truth, but that was the beginning of a nightmare.
Will the two be able to solve the case and return safely?
With “male bonding” as the main theme, the action scenes and human drama create great harmony, and the result is a feel-good entertainment for all.

title: N.Y. Maxman
synopsis:
The first Maxman, Seigi Taniguchi, is living in New York. He meets “N.Y. Maxman” aka “Hiro Max,” who is the grandson of the author of the comic series “Maxman.”
The two return to Japan and unite with the second Maxman, Hideo, at Japan TV. Meanwhile, an idol called Kaho is forced to retire from showbiz because of her father, who was arrested for terrorist activities. To get revenge, Kaho plans to accuse her father on a Japan TV show.
But on the night before the show, somebody kidnaps her.
Hiro transforms into Maxman and investigates the case.

title: Dance For Me
synopsis: DANCE FOR ME is a documentary film about two young and deeply passionate ballroom dancers whose ambition for success overshadows everything else.

title: Higher Brothers & HARIKIRI - Nothing Wrong
synopsis: MV of Nothing Wrong

title: Cicakman 2
synopsis: The evil Professor Klon is back, not only to overthrow the Government but also to control the world's supply of fresh water through his ingenious plan, "Black Water" and it’s up to Cicakman to stop him. However, he is also forced to face his personal dilemmas as he realized that his life is at stake as well.

title: Tuna Girl
synopsis: Minami is a junior at Kindai University's Faculty of Agriculture, Department of Fisheries. She heads to the university's Aquaculture Research Institute to learn about the one and only, """"full-cycle aquaculture"""" of Pacific bluefin tuna. Her classmates can't be more absorbed in the research, but Minami just can't see what's so great about it. However, as she spends time with her other classmates, her attitude gradually changes. That's when she's asked to do an interview for a program, but during that very interview, Minami's clumsiness puts her in great trouble...

title: Orange Girl
synopsis: THE ORANGE GIRL is about two young mens different paths to finding love. Based on Jostein Gaarder's ("Sophie's World") novel translated into 42 languages.

title: Magic Hour The Series 2 Characters Sneakpeak
synopsis: Rangga & Raina's love story now comes to an end. How about Gwenny, Troy, Tegar and Mitha? Now, it's time to peep the season 2 trailer!

title: The Watchers: The Last Hero
synopsis: In this installment of a four-part action adventure where four teens – the Watchers - fight the rich for justice, the body of man with the Watchers’ logo drop onto the deck of a boat during a wedding party. Is this a set-up or is there a new vigilante?

title: Full Metal Panic! 2nd Section – One Night Stand
synopsis: Encountered an aircraft accident in childhood and grew up in Afghanistan, Sergeant Sousuke Sagara is a special force member of the mysterious international organization— “Mithril”, who specially performs secret missions assigned by the organization around the world where is about to break out wars or armed clashes, to fight against terrorists, rescue hostages and solve all kinds of crisis. Now Sousuke’s latest mission is to leave for Japan as soon as possible and disguise as a high school student to slip into Jindai High School, in order to protect a 16 years old girl—Kaname Chidory. Kaname looks just like an ordinary high school girl, but for some reason she becomes the target of spies from all over the world. To protect Kaname, Sousuke drives the latest armor— “Arm Slave”, which just appeared on the battlefield in the late 80s, to confront other mysterious organizations.

title: Bukaan 8
synopsis: Alam and Mia, a millennial couple who meet and fall in love in cyberspace. Their relationship's never got approval by Mia's family because Alam is considered never take things seriously. At the moment of the birth of their first child, Alam wanted to prove to Ambu and Abah, Mia's parents, that he's a dream husband.

title: Cicakman
synopsis: Hairi (Saiful Apek) is a loser who lives in Metrofulus. While working in the lab, he accidentally drinks coffee that has been contaminated by a virus-infected gecko. He soon finds himself doing the most insane things, such as sticking to walls, making chirping cicak noises and adding bugs to his menu. He turns to his best friend and apartment mate, Danny (Yusry Abdul Halim), and begs him to find the reason behind his strange antics. Meanwhile, the people of Metrofulus are constantly being infected by new strains of viruses, and the only cure seems to come only from Professor Klon's (Aznil Nawawi) lab. Suspecting something amiss, Hairi and Danny launch their own investigation and discover that Professor Klon is not only the creator of such viruses, but also has a more sinister plan up his sleeve, backed by his business partners, the Ginger Boys Ramlie and AC Mizal, who first tend to take revenge on Professor Klon's failed experiment on them; making their senses turn abnormal.

title: Drop
synopsis: Fights, romance, bad friends...a masterpiece that goes beyond the norm! Starring two celebrated young actors, Hiroki Narimiya and Hiro Mizushima! They are an unbeatable team that sets fire to the world of “DROP”! Hiroshi, a wannabe delinquent, transfers from a private school to a public middle school and soon attracts the attention of delinquents. Summoned by them, he goes to a riverbank and finds Tatsuya, an evil-yet-charismatic delinquent. Before he knows it, Hiroshi is fighting Tatsuya. Tatsuya beats him up easily, but Hiroshi is allowed to join the gang.

title: Dead Of The Nite
synopsis: When a group of Internet sensation ghost hunters investigate the infamous Jericho Manor, they soon realize it's not just ghosts that go bump in the night! As each member of the team gets slaughtered, the remaining survivors need to discover who...or what is killing them before it is too late.

title: The Accidental Detective 2 In Action
synopsis: A comic-book shop owner and an ex-homicide detective struggle to find clients for their detective agency, until they’re hired to look into a suspicious death, which leads them to a broader conspiracy.

title: Sultan Agung: Tahta, Perjuangan, Cinta
synopsis: This is a story of Raden Mas Rangsang (Marthino Lio). After his father passed away, still a teenager, he have to take over his father throne and given the title of Sultan Agung Hanyakrakusuma. Sultan Agung (Ario Bayu) must unite all kingdom in Java that's being separated by VOC politics under JP Coen. On the other hand, he also have to sacrifice his true love to Lembayung (Adinia Wirasti) by marrying noble woman against his choices. During his war against VOC, Sultan Agung also have to face many treason against him.

title: Sesat
synopsis: Setelah kematian Papanya, Amara beserta Mama dan Adiknya, terpaksa pindah ke rumah kakeknya yang terletak di desa terpencil di tengah hutan. Dia menemukan kejanggalan di desa ini. Semua penduduk desa ternyata orang tua dan setiap matahari terbenam, para penduduk serentak keluar rumah membawa sesajen sambil mengucapkan sebuah mantra misterius. Belakangan, Amara mengetahui bahwa di desa ini terdapat sumur keramat yang konon bisa mengabulkan segala permintaan. Dia memanjatkan keinginannya untuk mengobrol dengan sang papa melalui sebuah ritual sakral memanggil setan penunggu sumur, Beremanyan. Apakah keinginan Amara akan terkabul ataukah hal lain yang justru menantinya?

title: The Amityville Terror
synopsis: When a new family moves to an old house in Amityville, they are tormented and tortured by an evil spirit living in the home while trapped by the malicious townspeople who want to keep them there.

title: Get Lost
synopsis: Ringgo, Nadia, pacar Ringgo, Vina, Anton, Bombom merencanakan petualangan seru saat mereka bolos sekolah. Di tengah perjalanan mereka harus memutar arah melalui jalan potong karena menghindari operasi polisi. Di tengah jalan pintas itu mobil mereka bermasalah dan mereka melihat sebuah bangunan tua: Benteng Pendem peninggalan Belanda. Karena sudah lelah mereka memutuskan istirahat malam itu di benteng tersebut. Ternyata jalan pintas yang mereka pilih juga memutar arah waktu. Ringgo merasa ada sesuatu yang berbeda di sekitar mereka dan terus menghantui kemana pun mereka berada.

title: Bangkit Berkuasa | Sebuah Filem KL Gangster Underworld
synopsis: Despite the underworld ruled by men, young May Wong proves she’s no fool. Through grit and ferocity, she becomes the Queen of Bangsar.

title: Beware the Gonzo
synopsis: When the rebel-minded Gonzo (Ezra Miller) is ousted from his school paper by very-popular editor Gavin (Jesse McCartney), he teams with the mysterious Evie (Zoe Kravitz) to start his own paper and turn the social hierarchy on its head.

title: The Ouija Exorcism
synopsis: In 1985, a celebrated exorcist trapped a horrific demon inside a ouija board. Thinking the board to be a game, his son played without obeying the rules, and let the demon loose. In order to save his son, the exorcist sent him far away until the demon could be destroyed. Thirty years later, and after his death, his grandson finds the board and makes the same mistake his father did. Now the evil is back and roaming the earth to terrorize those responsible for its imprisonment.

title: Cut Her Out
synopsis: Darcy Baker can't purge her mind of the animalistic abuse she suffered as a child at the hands of her mother. Darcy's therapist Ryan discovers that her family homestead has been abandoned. He is eager to get her back there and pull the suppressed memories to the surface. Their stay becomes deadly.

title: Liam dan Laila
synopsis: Terinspirasi oleh kisah nyata tentang kisah cinta dua insan beda negara, budaya dan agama. Laila, gadis Minang berusia 31 tahun, terhubung dengan dunia lewat layar laptopnya. Suatu hari, dia terlibat percakapan dengan Liam, pemuda asal Rouen, kota kecil di Prancis. Percakapan ini membawa Liam terbang ke Minang untuk menemui Laila. Kedatangan pemuda asing di kampung halaman Laila menjadi awal dari segala konflik yang akan dihadapi keduanya.

title: The Line
synopsis: One day, Yoon-jin finds a boy sitting in front of her house stairs. After some while, she again finds him still on the same place and offers the boy who says he has no keys to come inside her house and wait. As time passes, it gets dark and yet she hears nothing from boy’s parent.

title: Ang Kwento Nating Dalawa
synopsis: As clouds begin to roll, we see the morning life of a busy city. Cars jam the streets, as people makes squares of the side streets they walk on. People queues in line as everyone wants to board the city train. This is SAM’s daily picture of his long travel to school. He is a young filmmaker, who in his everyday commute, meets his girlfriend ISA, an aspiring writer, in a station, stops away from the school they go to. The gloomy weather seems to be painting the day for the young couple. The concurring problems between them loom as they try to survive the day. ISA is about to leave for the States after graduation and SAM gets an apprenticeship offer from one of the top film directors of the country. All these reasons make way for unspoken words of doubt and fear, on top of a bigger dilemma they have to face. SAM and ISA had to make a decision. They cannot stay too long in this relationship.

title: Knight Funny Video
synopsis: So should we really restrict playing pranks on April 1st only..Not really. Check out some of the funniest prank videos where visitors in public places just get fooled by the makers. Well in the end of every episode , all of them have a good fun while we laugh watching it.

title: 5 cm
synopsis: 5 orang sahabat: Genta, Arial, Zafran, Riani, dan Ian sepakat untuk berpisah sementara dan tidak berkomunikasi selama 3 bulan. Itu bukanlah hal yang mudah, mengingat mereka selalu bersama. Merayakan pertemuan mereka setelah 3 bulan berpisah, kelima sahabat ini merencanakan sebuah perjalanan yang penuh dengan impian dan tantangan.

title: Eunhee
synopsis: Eunhee posts a lie on her SNS without any reason. All the people around her begin to give attention to her and she likes it. But her lie circulates in unintentional way.

title: Ikut Aku Ke Neraka
synopsis: The happiness of Lita and her husband Rama do not last long because Lita is often terrorized by creepy female creatures. Rama brings Mr. Adam to clean their house from the ghost disturbance. Mr Adam explaines that this terror does not come from the house but from inside Lita herself. Mr Adam gives a hint that the answer is in Lita's past, by asking for an explanation from Sari, the mother she left behind. Sari is admitted to a mental hospital.

title: Armor Hero (Atlas) Movie 2014
synopsis: The UCP Control Centre that holds multiple people infected with the Ocasian virus was seized by the Princes of Ocasers, Lambda and Phi, and they used them to build an army of Ocasers. Duanmu, Qingshan, Kuohai, and Ke Sheng donned the six super armors Atlas, Techno, Lava, Tornado, Tsunami, and Clif to strike back at the Ocasers. But unknown to them, the two princes are brooding yet another evil plan.

title: When I See You Again
synopsis: There's something between a guy and a girl but they are not in a relationship as they are afraid to lose a friend. Can you cherish your loved ones in your life?

title: Hit & Run
synopsis: Tegar Saputra, a celebrity policeman who has his own reality show, is assigned to arrest Coki, a drug kingpin who has just escaped from prison. Unfortunately this time Tegar must be paired with Lio, a conman. Tegar, who is used to acting alone, now has to try to complete his mission with Lio, which makes it difficult instead. Tegar's and Lio's search for Coki are accompanied by Meisa, a singer, and Jefri.

title: Jailangkung 2
synopsis: Tasya watches an old video showing her father communicating with her late mother through Jailangkung. She then creates her own Jailangkung in hope to meet her mother who passed away after the laboring process. Unfortunately, her action resulted in the appearance of evil spirit who terrorizes her family. Bella & Rama, with the help of a new friend, Bram, once again have to save their family from evil spirit.

title: Ai-chan, The Teen Detective From Yoshimoto Shinkigeki
synopsis:
“A truly beautiful girl is a girl with a good heart.”
Ai grew up into a kind teenager, believing in what her late mother told her.
Beautiful girls are her enemies; her past trauma made her think that pretty girls are mean.
One day, she receives a mission to protect the pop idol group NMB48 from a bomb threat.
Going undercover to be surrounded by cute girls is a nightmare for Ai, but she cannot abandon her mission.
And so this unprecedented undercover search begins, where Ai has to sing and dance her way to catch the bomber with her 100 kg body...©2017 Yoshimoto Kogyo.

title: The Aimless Bullet
synopsis: A high school kid pays a visit to his bully carrying a bag with a bomb in it.

title: Keluarga Cemara
synopsis: After his house and all of his treasure are confiscated by the debt collector, thanks to his brother-in-law's debt, Abah is very determined to withstand all of this by staying temporarily in a house in a remote village in West Java. It is his childhood house, inherited by his father. Abah then had to get use to his new economy status along with his little family: Emak, Euis who was stepping into adolescent, also Cemara/Ara who is a high-spirited child. They also have to face problems inside their own family which slowly shake the family's principle: "the most valuable treasure is family."

title: Middle School Student A
synopsis: Haejun has been no. 1 in his middle school in Gangbuk, but his family moves to Daechi to go to a better high school. Eunseo has always been no. 1 in her school but Haejun takes her place as soon as he enters the new school. The students including Eunseo, Nayeon decide to shake Haejun up and try to drop his rank. Taejun develops feelings for Eunseo and gets attacked by the other students...

title: Street
synopsis: Remo Street is a young fighter who comes from a world where nothing is easy. So when he is faced with the opportunity to train with a world class coach, he has to choose between the long hard road to honor and glory, or succumbing to a brutal future as a cage fighter for the Russian Mafia.

title: Menunggu Pagi
synopsis: Attending an event like Djakarta Warehouse Project is never a priority or option for Bayu, a boy who works in a small vynil store, not even his bestfriends can convince him to go. But his mind changes after meeting a girl named Sarah. There's something about her that makes him curious and even falls for her.

title: Born To Kill: Myra Hindley
synopsis: Depicted by the tabloid press as ""the most hated woman in Britain"", the crimes committed by Hindley and her lover, Ian Brady, shocked the nation and became the benchmark by which other acts of evil came to be measured. Until she met Brady, Hindley had been, by all accounts, a perfectly normal girl, with strong religious feelings. She loved children and animals, and was much in demand as a babysitter. But when they became lovers, Hindley was prepared to do anything Brady asked…Can people be persuaded to kill for love? Were they crimes of passion? Brady claimed that Hindley was a manipulative liar who was as committed to murder as he had been…

title: Cicakman 3
synopsis: Seven years after the events of Cicakman 2: Planet Hitam, the former superhero of Metrofulus is missing. With speculations that Cicakman is either dead or retired, SuperBro steps in to take his place, claiming to be the new defender of Metrofulus. The question is, can we trust him?

title: KL Gangster 2
synopsis: Malek and Jai weren’t always part of the underworld. They were from a normal family and everything was well. That is until their father passed away, and they inherited his debt from a loan shark. Gangsters aren’t born, they’re made.

title: The Photographers
synopsis: Ayoung going to a slum to take some photos. After taking a picture of a granny, weird whistles chase her constantly. She finds mysterious things one by one in the town. Feeling nervous but she never stops taking photos. Finally a boy appears in front of her.

title: Angel Of Justice Head Money
synopsis: Quadriplegic, Jan, wants to be discharged from the clinic against medical advice. Doctor turned attorney, Dr Engel, fights his doctor who happens to be her father. Meanwhile she also takes on a dodgy clinic more intent on making money than saving lives.

title: My Gaming Dream
synopsis: The son wished to be successful in gaming field but his father did not support him. The father slowly understood that his son was not playing games for fun. He learned that his son could achieve great success if he worked hard.

title: Africa’s Super 7
synopsis: On the northern bank of the Sand River in the Mala-Mala Game Reserve in South Africa, seven magnificent creatures reside in an area the size of Manhattan Island. Tracking them for 24 hours we reveal the invisible threads that bind them together in a never-ending daily drama.

title: Blind Spot
synopsis: Photographer Stephanie and her boyfriend Eric spend winter in the Caribbean where a serial killer is on the loose. When Stephanie snaps shots of an altercation between a truck driver and a young woman, the couple unwittingly becomes targets of a madman.

title: Pengejar Angin
synopsis: Dapunta, pemuda asal Lahat, Sumatera Selatan, mendapat julukan pengejar angin berkat kemampuannya berlari cepat. Dia sedang mengalami dilema. Sang ibu ingin dia melanjutkan pendidikannya, sementara ayahnya ingin dia mengikuti jejaknya sebagai bajing loncat (perampok truk). Dengan dukungan sahabat, guru, dan cinta pertamanya, dia memutuskan untuk mengikuti kata hatinya melanjutkan kuliah. Jalan pun terbuka, saat ada pelatih lari nasional asal Jakarta yang melihat bakatnya. Namun, untuk mencapai mimpinya dia harus menghadapi ayahnya, teman sekolahnya yang membenci dirinya akibat profesi sang ayah, dan juga rival utamanya Jusuf, yang juga cerdas dan berbakat.

title: The Secret Agent Club
synopsis: To the world Ray Chase is nothing more than a klutzy, overgrown toy seller whose wife passed away a few years ago; and his only son Jeremy doesn't get to see him very often, because he's always away on "business trips." What no one knows-not even Jeremy-is that his dad is a secret agent who flies all around the world, completing highly classified missions for a top-secret peacekeeping agency.

title: Ramadan: Message from the UN Secretary-General
synopsis: On the occasion of Ramadan, UN Video is pleased to present a video message from the United Nations Secretary-General António Guterres.

title: The Outlaws
synopsis: Jang Chen (Yoon Kye-Sang) came from China and now works as a loan shark in a seedy Chinatown area of Seoul. He's backed up by his bloodthirsty henchmen Wei Sung-Rak (Jin Seon-Kyu) and Yang-Tae (Kim Sung-Kyu). Jang Chen is beyond brutal in his methods to collect money. Meanwhile, Ma Suk-Do (Ma Dong-Seok) is a detective in the Chinatown area of Seoul. He tries to keep the peace, while two Chinese-Korean gangs battle over turf in the neighborhood. Jang Chen makes his move to take over.

title: Bros. Maxman
synopsis: Hideo’s big brother is Seigi Taniguchi, aka Maxman. He returns from Indonesia, and is looking for a job. Seigi has been transferred to New York, and Hideo has no idea that Maxman is his brother. He joins Japan TV and meets Rina Igarashi, an upperclassman who rejected him in high school. Hideo is struck by how cute Rina looks. At work, he is constantly being told off by the producer and his senior director. One day, he finds a small piece of a meteor in his brother’s room and wears it as a necklace, not knowing that that is the source of Maxman’s power.©2016 Bros Maxman Production Partnership.

title: Nothing But The Bests
synopsis: Nothing But the Bests! is a ROM-COM starring a collective cast of new and seasoned talent. 4 friends rent a VIP island resort during storm season in hopes to save some money on their wedding.

title: All American Bikini Car Wash
synopsis: An enterprising college student agrees to run his professor's Las Vegas car wash to avoid flunking out of school. But it's Vegas gone wild when he decides to staff it with gorgeous bikini-clad girls.

title: Master And Apprentice
synopsis:
Master Zhong established a popular handmade noodle shop. Unfortunately, he hurt his right hand in an accident, therefore he's unable to make noodles again. Master Zhong was devastated and his business was deteriorating.
Ah Lin, Master Chong's apprentice, used to be a lazybone. Seeing Master Zhong's condition awaken the passion for cooking in her. She finally persuaded Master Zhang to pull himself together and they managed to save the business.

title: Sang Kiai
synopsis: Kisah tentang penjajahan Jepang Tahun 1942 yg melarang pengibaran bendera merah putih, melarang lagu Indonesia Raya dan memaksa rakyat Indonesia untuk melakukan Sekerei. KH Hasyim Asyari menolak melakukan Sekerei karena tindakan itu menyimpang dari aqidah agama Islam yang hanya boleh menyembah kepada Allah SWT. Karena tindakan berani itu, KH Hasyim Asyari ditangkap Jepang.  Harun, salah satu santri KH Hasyim Asyari, melakukan demo menuntut kebebasan KH Hasyim Asyari. Sedangkan salah satu putranya KH Wahid Hasyim, berusaha mencari jalan damai untuk membebaskan KH Hasyim Asyari.

title: Desert Coffee
synopsis: In California’s poorest desert region, a colourful group of regulars and their dogs gather at Rob’s cafe for coffee in ‘the last free place in America’. Slab City is a squatter community in the Sonoran Desert, Southern California. The inhabitants, Slabbers, live in broken trailers or old school buses. Their closest neighbors are the United States Navy and Marine Corps, who practice aerial bombing in the area. Despite living off-grid in extreme weather conditions with no running water, electricity, sewage system or trash pickup, the residents enthusiastically embrace their freedom in the beautiful badlands of the desert. Rob hates coffee but as soon as dawn breaks he meticulously brews ‘the best coffee in the county’ for the customers of his makeshift cafe. Desert Coffee sketches an intimate, warm portrait of Rob and his friends – an unforgettable bunch of troubled characters and left-behinds.

title: Jelena
synopsis: 'Jelena' chronicles the career and training regimen of 8-time world champion boxer Jelena Mrdjenovich as she prepares for her 48th pro fight against undefeated European champion Gaelle Amand.

title: Love In Vienna
synopsis: Melody, a production assistant, is instructed to locate and convince pianist Michael Grimaud, who fell off the radar ten years ago, to play at a concert. She finds him in the Austrian Alps where he has retired but things get tricky when sparks fly.

title: Modus
synopsis: Andovi begitu tergila-gila dengan Kirana, gadis cantik pujaan hatinya. Dia meminta bantuan sang kakak, Jovial, untuk mendekati gadis pujaannya. Selain dibantu kakaknya yang playboy dan berpengalaman dalam urusan menaklukkan wanita, dia juga mendapat bantuan dari sahabat-sahabatnya. Cara dan saran mereka yang gila dan aneh pastinya tidak membantu Andovi mendapatkan Kirana. Ditambah lagi dengan kehadiran cowok baru yang menjadi saingannya, Dipa. Akankah perjuangan Andovi merebut hati Kirana berbuah manis?

title: In The Dark Half
synopsis: A soulful and scary, psychological horror film about a teenage girl's journey through her own haunted imagination.

title: Preman Pensiun The Movie
synopsis: This is a story about Kang Mus who has switched professions from the thug world. The ex-subordinates of Kang Mus are now live on the right path. Until one day, Gobang, one of Kang Mus' people, did not accept it when his brother was beaten into coma, thus planned to take revenge on the culprit by asking for help from other ex-thugs without Kang Mus' knowledge. Does this mean Kang Mus will return to his previous life? Meanwhile, Kang Mus became alarmed when his beloved teenage daughter, Safira, starts dating. As a father, he'll do anything to protect her daughter and this starts another kind of war in Kang Mus' life.

title: Explicit Innocence
synopsis: To 19-year-old Cha Junho, there’s something much more urgent than his grades, future dreams, or college. It is to lose his virginity. He begs and pleads his girlfriend Seogyeong, but why is the world so cruel? She seems willing at one moment but then backs off. Will Junho’s wish come true before the year is over?

title: The Five Star Stories
synopsis: Ladios Sopp is heading towards Bastogne where the presentation of two newly awakened fatimas is about to occur. Fatimas are androids designed to be mandatory co-pilots of giant robots called mortal headds. Both fatimas are acquaintaces of Sopp and during their introduction it is expected that they choose the pilots with whom they shall become partners of.

title: K2 - Touching The Sky
synopsis: The children of acclaimed alpinists who lost their lives on K2, are taken on an expedition to the Himalayan mountains to face their parents'  fatal destiny.

title: Kais Pre Summer
synopsis: Sokai finds that his teacher is quitting her job. Sokai is so sad about that and plans to give her a present before she leave the school. In order to buy a present, he tries to do his best walking around here and there. Finally the teacher leaves him, but he let his feeling go on his own. In fact, a bigger farewell is ahead of him.

title: The Immortal Wars: Resurgence
synopsis: The freedom war between Dominion and the rebels has just begun. Trikalypse joins forces with the rebel leader and her team of freedom fighters. They must now fight back to bring Dominion down and expose him to the world.

title: London Love Story 3
synopsis:
After spending time together for two years, Dave decides to marry Caramel. They travel to Bali where Caramel is reminded of her past. 
Dave and Caramel face a tragedy that changes their lives.

title: Never Forget
synopsis: The son wished to be successful in gaming field but his father did not support him. The father slowly understood that his son was not playing games for fun. He learned that his son could achieve great success if he worked hard.

title: Dancing in The Rain
synopsis: Banyu lives with his grandmother who has been nurturing him since a kid because his parents abandoned him. He has an autism spectrum disorder, therefore it's difficult for him to interact with others. One day, Radin defended him from bullies, and it starts a beautiful friendship between them. Other than that, Kinara comes into the picture and becomes friend with them. Their friendship is put to a test once love has entered the equation. Will their relationship survive?

title: Dark Moon Rising
synopsis: Small-town girl meets mysterious drifter boy, they fall in love. Only in this case, the boy brings with him a family curse and unimaginable horror that rains hell upon the small town.

title: Ravenswood
synopsis: When 4 American tourists - Sofia, Carl, Belle and Michael - go on a ghost tour, they get much more than they bargained for, when the ghosts of an evil Doctor and his last patient victim trap them in the old abandoned psychiatric ward.

title: Karak
synopsis: Four students (Sheera Ayob, Shahir Zawawi, Along Eyzendy, Kilafairy) are heading back to their college in Kuantan after a night out in Kuala Lumpur, when they encounter massive traffic jam on the Karak highway. In an attempt to make it back in time for their classes in the morning, they decide to exit the highway and take an alternative route back to Kuantan via the old single carriageway trunk road, not knowing that this decision would alter their lives forever.

title: Blood Widow
synopsis: After buying a nice house in the country, Laurie and Hugh, a successful young couple, throw a party for their friends. During the wild night a few friends decide to explore the abandoned and decaying boarding school next door, only to wake an emotionally broken killer: The Blood Widow.

title: Pinch (2015)
synopsis: A light-fingered teen attempts to rip off a major drug syndicate to pay for his Mother's life saving surgery.

title: The Last Cavemen
synopsis: In 1978, the world found out about the existence of a previously undiscovered tribe, the Taaw’t Bato: a few hundred individuals hidden in the heart of the jungle on the Philippine island of Palawan. During the rainy season, they hide for months in giant natural caves to protect themselves from the typhoons. While there, they survive by fishing and hunting bats. But the Philippine government quickly came to the conclusion that these semi-nomadic people needed to be made sedentary. Gradually leaving the jungle and the caves behind, the Taaw’t Bato discovered urban life – and extreme poverty. Yet, over the past few years, dozens of sedentary Taaw’t Bato families have made a radical choice: unable to fit into this new environment, they have decided to leave the city, return to the land of their ancestors and settle there forever. We will follow the incredible journey of one such family, which has chosen to embark on this journey back to the jungle. The elders will revive ancestral customs; the youths will have to learn everything. For all of them, this will be a huge challenge: to survive the rainy season, they must make it all the way to the caves, their last refuge.

title: Rampant
synopsis: Prince of Joseon, Lee Chung, returns home after being taken hostage to the Qing Dynasty for more than 10 years. Soon, he fights against "Night Demons" that run rampant in the night to save the nation.

title: Ghost Note
synopsis: While rebellious teen Mallory is forced to stay with her grandmother while her parents vacation, she uncovers a paranormal family secret. Mallory accidentally sets the evil spirit of jazz musician Eugene Burns free, and now she must figure out a way to stop him before it's too late.

title: School's Out
synopsis: It's their big day: School's out for the 18-year old Lucas, his confidante Alice, Richard the playboy and Maxime, the surprising Casanova of the gang.

title: A Somewhat Gentle Man
synopsis: Ulrik has no special wishes and makes no demands. He has killed some people, but this sort of stuff is part of the job when working in the criminal world...

title: Orang Kaya Baru
synopsis: This is a story about sudden wealth. Tika, Duta, Dodi, and their mother used to live simple lives as they are. When his father died, it was revealed that apparently all this time his father was a wealthy man. They also get inheritance in the form of assets that they never imagined. The family is now trying to enjoy their abundant wealth. Will their weatlh be a blessing or turns into a tough test for this family?

title: Love In Jaipur
synopsis: Anne and Francois plan to get hitched in Jaipur. She is tasked with bringing his mother’s urn of ashes to India but loses it along the way. Lost and desperate, she meets Ravi, a Franco-Indian, who helps her search for it but feelings develop between them.

title: Wolves
synopsis: Wolves tells the remarkable story of one of the world's most tenacious species and our closest fellow predator. The film follows these elusive subjects across remote landscapes in an effort to catch glimpses of a way of life known only to a handful of scientists.

title: Wah!Banana: Lies We Tell Ourselves
synopsis: We don't care about the number of views/likes/shares.

title: I Love You Masbro
synopsis: The Salman family has four children, all boys: Bagus, he's handsome but anxious around girls; Alim who always makes trouble; Rizky who's rather slow, and Vina, a pretty boy who is obsessed with K-style. Their parents pass away due to an accident while trying to pick Alim home from prison, so the Salman  children have to live independently without their parents. It turns out their parents have debts to the gangster who threatened Alim. The Salman family's efforts to make money start a quarrel between them. The gangster boss who runs out of patience, sends his men to kidnap Alia, Alim's lover. Alim decides ask for a help from someone from his dark past.

title: The Socratic Method
synopsis: Set in a fictional law school and written by a California attorney, the independent Comedy feature "The Socratic Method" follows the exploits of three first-year law students as they stagger their way through the pressure cooker that is legal education in America.

title: You're Pretty Oh Manbok
synopsis: Manbok lost her real parents and is living with her adoptive family. The family members treat her like their real daughter and sister so Manbok doesn't feel lonely at all. But she wants to see her real father for once. One day, she sees a singer sing a song her mom used to sing for her on TV and thinks the person who gave the song to the singer is her real father. She heads off to Chuncheon to find him. The man Manbok meets in Chuncheon has all the aspects of a perfect father but he doesn't seem to recognize Manbok. Also she finds out that he's soon to be married. After thinking hard, she goes to the wedding hall. Manbok's family finds out about this and goes to find her at the wedding hall.

title: Pertaruhan
synopsis: Four brothers Ibra, Elzan, Amar, and Ical attempting to collect money for their father's medical expense and ended up taking a very reckless decision.

title: Red Mercury
synopsis: In the 90s the ex-soviet republic of Estonia is the top metal exporter in the world. Thriller based on a true story about a criminal business and a merciless fight.

title: Love In Lapland
synopsis: Charlotte, a bankruptcy manager, is sent to Sweden to shut down a toy-making company. There, she meets Martial, the company’s CEO who lives like an idealist dreamer. She soon forgets about her agenda as she rediscovers her lust for life and love.

title: Journey To The West From Yoshimoto Shinkigeki
synopsis:
Sanzohoshi, Son Goku, Sa Gojo, and Cho Hakkai are on a journey seeking the scriptures that will bring happiness to all. The team carry on traveling by foot with a smile, but there is one small man—no, a creature—who is staring at them intensely. He is a creature known as the Big Cobra, who conspires to drink Sanzohoshi’s blood to gain 3,000 years of life. He has previously had an epic battle with the team and was utterly defeated. Now he’s back for revenge, waiting for the right moment. And finally, Big Cobra casts magic on them, making them travel to the future!
©2015 Yoshimoto Kogyo

title: Lalamera, The Ultimate Battle
synopsis: Lamalera: a remote village of 2 500 people on the southern coast of Indonesia. In this hostile land where nothing grows, people have managed to survive only thanks to a spectacular age-old hunt: the traditional and sacred harpooning of sperm whales. Despite danger and hard lives, the villagers have always been self-sufficient, living according to their traditions, far from globalization. But today, this balance is about to be broken. As people from a neighboring island start fishing with dynamite, the whales are disappearing. With no more whales to hunt, Lamalera is dying. In order to survive and feed their families, some villagers decide to embrace modernity and start using motors to fish further away from the island. But others want to preserve their traditional way of life at all costs, leading to a serious conflict of generations. Ancient social codes are falling apart. «Everybody for himself» is becoming the new model. Meanwhile, environmental protectionists are getting worried about overfishing and plan to turn the area into a natural reserve. What can we imagine for the last whale hunters? When globalization strikes and people are torn between the preservation of traditions and the need for modernity, discover how an entire village has to confront a new kind of battle, an ultimate battle—for their survival.

title: Deadman Inferno
synopsis: Munakata, a yakuza clan boss, Takeshi, and Shinya are attacked by rival yakuza, and Takeshi is sent to prison. Ten years later, Munakata is running a company while taking care of Takeshi’s daughter, Hinata. Takeshi is released, but finds out that Hinata has run off to Z Island. Meanwhile, Akira has also run away to Z Island with drugs. A mysterious disease spreads on the island, likely caused by Akira's homemade drug. He injects himself with the drug and dies...but comes back to life! He starts attacking the locals, infecting them with the disease. ©2015 "Z Island" Film Partners.

title: One Third
synopsis: Shu, the manager of the hostess club Honey Bunny; Kozi, the club’s waiter; and Ken, the club's regular; rob a bank. They have arranged to divide the 160 million yen, but there seems to be a disagreement about how to split the money. On top of that, there are those who are conspiring to steal the money: Maria, the most popular hostess at Honey Bunny; Hamasho, the extremely violent owner of the club; and Tamiko Shibugaki, aka “the witch of Kawasaki” who is a legendary loan shark. Who is the real mastermind? Where will the money go? And who will laugh at the end?

title: Full Metal Panic! 1st Section – Boy Meet Girl
synopsis: Encountered an aircraft accident in childhood and grew up in Afghanistan, Sergeant Sousuke Sagara is a special force member of the mysterious international organization— “Mithril”, who specially performs secret missions assigned by the organization around the world where is about to break out wars or armed clashes, to fight against terrorists, rescue hostages and solve all kinds of crisis. Now Sousuke’s latest mission is to leave for Japan as soon as possible and disguise as a high school student to slip into Jindai High School, in order to protect a 16 years old girl—Kaname Chidory. Kaname looks just like an ordinary high school girl, but for some reason she becomes the target of spies from all over the world. To protect Kaname, Sousuke drives the latest armor— “Arm Slave”, which just appeared on the battlefield in the late 80s, to confront other mysterious organizations.

title: Beautiful World
synopsis: A tragic school mishap leaves their only son brain dead. But, was it really an accident? The family sets out to investigate the truth.

title: If We Were A Season
synopsis: Two high school students were born and raised together as neighbors. This boy and girl are more like a married couple. They don’t say it, but they are precious to each other. Then one day, a new student appears. Unlike these two who don’t express their hearts, he’s brave and bold in expressing his feelings. He was enough to shake up the relationship of these two students. It was when everything was yet immature and clumsy. Let’s think about our forgotten past.

title: Talk Of The Devil
synopsis: Ruthless real estate agent Pasha conned an old lady of her mansion. The very next day, he demolishes it as the land would fetch him a fortune. Infuriated, the old lady curses Pasha and from now on he is damned to appear whenever someone talks of him!

title: Full Metal Panic! 3rd Section – Into the Blue
synopsis: Encountered an aircraft accident in childhood and grew up in Afghanistan, Sergeant Sousuke Sagara is a special force member of the mysterious international organization— “Mithril”, who specially performs secret missions assigned by the organization around the world where is about to break out wars or armed clashes, to fight against terrorists, rescue hostages and solve all kinds of crisis. Now Sousuke’s latest mission is to leave for Japan as soon as possible and disguise as a high school student to slip into Jindai High School, in order to protect a 16 years old girl—Kaname Chidory. Kaname looks just like an ordinary high school girl, but for some reason she becomes the target of spies from all over the world. To protect Kaname, Sousuke drives the latest armor— “Arm Slave”, which just appeared on the battlefield in the late 80s, to confront other mysterious organizations.

title: Kawin Kontrak 3
synopsis: Kawin kontrak 3 menceritakan tentang tiga sekawan yang mengalami nasib buruk dalam kesehariannya sehingga harus melakukan kawin kontrak.

title: I Came For This Dish
synopsis: On "I Came For This Dish" travels in search of local delicacies. In this episode, he comes to Hokkaido on his own, and we get a glimpse of how he interacts with kind-hearted locals and experiences the great nature surrounding him. Come see Japan on this program that unfolds like a "novel in motion." On this episode, the local specialty that Matayoshi is after is: corned beef from Kosmos Farm in Tokachi, Hokkaido. It's corned beef that defies all expectations, and paired with a fresh, raw egg, makes for the ultimate egg & rice bowl! He also encounters a mysterious sign, some mouthwatering curry, and special crème caramel! Come join Matayoshi on his journey as he makes some interesting stops on the way.

title: Race For Glory
synopsis: Stock car racing is one of America's most popular sports with more than 75 million fans nationwide, and growing. For many racers, the winning values of team, family and faith inspire them on and off the track. Featuring never-before-seen interviews with some of the sport's most popular personalities - including Danica Patrick, Juan Pablo Montoya, Jamie McMurray and Chip Ganassi - Race for Glory is an in-depth look at the sport's road to victory!

title: Kuntilanak 2 (2019)
synopsis: Dinda who sucessfully escaped from Kuntilanak's terrors, wanted to meet her biological mother, without permission from her aunt. On the way to her mother's home, she and her siblings experienced many strange things. Dinda again has to deal with Kuntilanak, but it was different from what she had defeated using spikes or spells.

title: Zombie Wars
synopsis: A rebel leads an uprising against a zombie horde that harvests humans for food.

title: Tough Rides: India
synopsis: Ryan Pyle and Colin Pyle get a chance to ride through some of the most stunning parts of India as part of their motorcycle expedition and television production.

title: The Red Teacher
synopsis: “Girls, Desire What is Forbidden!” The place setting of this story is a girls’ high school of Gyongsang Province in 1985. To the main character Sunduk, her homeroom teacher Taenam is a perverted devil. An old bachelor of a rather stubborn nature, he tends to suppress the spontaneity of his students who have reached puberty showing a great deal of curiosity about sex. Because he exercises clout as a trusted man of the vice principal of the school, he is despised by all the students. None of them likes him. . He is a sorry fellow, however, who knows nothing about romance as he has never dated anyone. All he does well is yelling and shouting at his students. One day he discovers “Red Book, Vol. 1” at a local store. It is a bawdy sort of fiction, therefore banned by the government. But it spreads among the school girls quickly enough. The story ends quite abruptly with a terse note saying To be continued. Everybody is curious as to how the sequence will unfold, but no one knows where the second volume is. Sunduk decides to write the second edition herself on behalf of her friends dying to know the ending. Being a curious George himself, Taenam overlooks her clandestine project. How will the Red Book turmoil be resolved?

title: Manie - Manie
synopsis: A girl and her cat fall through a looking-glass into a dark labyrinth full of strange people.In the distant future, a tough racer uses his psychokinetic powers against his opponents during his final race. A snooty salaryman is sent by his bosses to the jungle to stop a completely automated construction job, and spends several days there arguing with the robots.

title: The Butcher Possessions
synopsis: When Chris Shaw takes his friends out to an isolated house to make a web video, they summon an evil spirit and must fight for survival once it begins to hunt them down.

title: ILY From 38,000 Ft
synopsis: When Aletta heads to Bali for a holiday, she meets Arga and they fall head over heels in love. They spent every waking moment with each other in Bali and then the time came for Aletta to return to Jakarta. Arga promises to find her and marry her. But to her surprise, he never shows up. Was it all a lie, or did something happen to him?

title: The Gift (2018)
synopsis: When writer Tiana unexpectedly falls in love with Harun, a visually impaired man, on her 30th birthday, she has no clue that her orphanage friend, Arie, was going to propose to her on the same day. Caught between two men, she fails to handle the situation which ends up with Harun breaking off the relationship and more so, Tiana becomes uncertain about who she is and what she wants in life. She runs away from Harun to be with Arie and starts new life in Florence. But somehow, destiny will bring both broken hearts back again.

title: Dance To Death
synopsis: In Russia's own version of Hunger Games, the energy of teens is used to power the city after a nuclear apocalypse. Two youngsters forced to battle each other in a dance off to determine who is sacrificed fall in love instead. Can they escape?

title: The Watchers: Jack Pot
synopsis: In the final part of a four-part action adventure where the teen Watchers fight for justice, the team is asked to help a man who has fallen in with the wrong crowd. They discover an underground casino where the rich gamble using the lives of the poor.

title: Something In Between
synopsis: Gema, a high school teenager, falls in love with Maya, and tries to make every effort to conquer his heart. However, their love must be tested with the challenge of reaching a dream and also the presence of a third person.

title: Abang Long Fadil
synopsis: Abang Long Fadil, a man who constantly dreams that his life is that of a gangster. But when his best friend, Malik goes to prison, then more chaos ensues and daydreaming may not be too far off from reality.

title: Mr. Maxman
synopsis:
Seigi Taniguchi is an anchorman for Japan TV. Inspired by his father who loved comics, Seigi used to dream of becoming a superhero. But finding out that his secret crush, Yuko Tsujimura, is aspiring to be a journalist, he decides to follow the same path. He gets a job with Japan TV, but one day, he makes a terrible mistake while reading the news. His boss orders him to host a show with the prime minister, saying that if he makes a mistake, he will be transferred to another department. He is put to the test, but his destiny starts to change.
©2015“Mr.Maxman” Production Committee.

title: Santa With Muscles
synopsis: Penurious but muscle-bound Blake Thorne has made a vast fortune marketing health food and health supplements. He once was a nice fellow, but as his wealth increases, he becomes increasingly self-centered and decadent. One day, he gets in a great paint-gun fight that goes too far. Blake escapes the cops by running into a shopping mall, quickly donning a Santa Suit and pretending to be St. Nick. A head injury causes Blake to suffer amnesia, and an opportunistic "elf" decides to convince Blake that he is indeed Santa. This leads "Santa" to help save an orphanage, filled with adorable moppets, from the machinations of a greedy, insane doctor.

title: Lily Grace: A Witch Story
synopsis: After the death of his estranged father, Ron returns to his childhood home. His first night there he is visited by a supernatural being. Haunted by feelings of guilt, convinced this entity has something to do with his father's passing, he stays to uncover the truth behind the witch named Lily Grace.

title: Relationshit
synopsis: Alitt penulis buku best seller, didukung Wina kekasihnya, sejak dia bukan apa-apa. Hubungan itu kandas karena Wina lebih menuruti permintaan ibunya untuk berpisah dari Wina hingga membuat hidup Alitt hampa. Alitt bertemu dengan Vivi (Natasha Wilona). Vivi mampu membuat Alitt berpaling dari Wina. Tetapi, Wina datang kembali dan membuat Alitt bimbang.

title: Alaska: Spirit of The Wild
synopsis: "Alaska: Spirit of the Wild" transports viewers on a voyage into the last great frontier where nature enchants the eye with magnificent spectacles. Viewers will find themselves fishing with brown bears, soaring with bald eagles, dodging calving glaciers, and racing on the hooves of caribou.

title: The Perfect Husband
synopsis: In Seconds, Ayla's highschool time will be a mess when, suddenly, Arsen comes to introduce him as her future husband. This event makes her relation with Ando, her boyfriend, in jeopardy. Ayla is mad with her father, Tio, for matchmaking her without her consent. Meanwhile, Arsen won't give up to win Ayla's heart.

title: Broke Into The Village At Night
synopsis: Six-undergrads break into a remote village that is shrouded in mystery and smoke. Their presence brings about strange events that will lead them to uncovering the mysteries behind the village.

title: Mortal Affair
synopsis: Sasha, a beautiful, young photographer, finds her lover, a successful artist, murdered. The police suspect her and the killers want to silence her. She goes on the run from all as she tries to solve this mystery.

title: The Immortal Wars
synopsis: Set in the future the world has been split into sectors, humans have captured deviants and force them to fight to the death. Madman Dominion Harvey hosts the immortal wars and televises the show to the entire planet. Trikalypse and fellow deviants will not only fight to survive, but to bring down Dominion Industries.

title: Pariban Idola dari Tanah Jawa
synopsis: Moan adalah pemuda Batak yang sudah lama tinggal di Jakarta. Meski usianya sudah menginjak 37 tahun, ia belum memiliki pacar. Melihat situasi ini, ibu Moan memaksa putranya pulang dan menikah dengan Uli, sepupunya. Rupanya, Uli telah memiliki kekasih. Bagaimana akhir kisah pemuda batak ini bersama Paribannya.

title: Ngenest
synopsis: Nasib menentukan  Ernest lahir di sebuah keluarga Cina. Bullying menjadi makanan sehari-hari. Ia berupaya untuk berbaur dengan teman-teman pribuminya, Sayangnya, berbagai upaya yang ia lakukan tidak berhasil, hingga Ernest berkesimpulan bahwa cara terbaik untuk bisa membaur adalah dengan menikahi seorang perempuan pribumi.

title: Surau dan Silek
synopsis: This is a story of friendship and family based on Minangkabau culture. Adil, an orphaned boy, is ambitious to win the silat championship. Previously he lost due to being cheated by his arch enemy. Assisted by two good friends, Daya and Kurip, The Three have to face various challenges to the long-awaited victory.

title: Travel Tales
synopsis: Samridhhi Rai travels with her celebrity friends to Dhulikhel for a fun and adventure trip.

title: Travel Tales 2
synopsis: Samridhhi Rai travels to Chitwan with three stand up comedians for a fun filled adventure.

title: Nightblade
synopsis: When three childhood friends are brought back together after years apart, a string of mysterious and brutal "Jack The Ripper" inspired murders erupt, pitting the friends against a killer with an obsession for death.

title: Interval
synopsis: A young man and woman are confined in a huge abandoned building. One must watch over the other. She is a captive and he is forced by the local mobster to be her jailer.

title: Magic Hour
synopsis: Raina is in dilemma when she met Dimas, an interesting yet ignorant man who captured her attention. As they become closer, Toby (Raina's childhood friend) suddenly proclaimed his love to Raina. On the other side, Dimas is already set up with Gwenny, who in fact is Raina's best friend. Now Raina is faced with a difficult options, her friendship of her love?

title: The Viking Maid
synopsis: Despite record salmon runs in the state of Alaska, wild Salmon fishermen struggle to stay afloat in the flooded salmon markets of the world. This documentary is a journey aboard an Alaskan salmon seining vessel, exploring the lifestyle and adventure of a dying breed of men, the last of hunters and gatherers who dare to take on mother nature to earn a living. Journey aboard the Viking Maid, atop the erratic seas of Southeast Alaska, and find out why you should always ask, "is this salmon farmed or wild?"

title: Magbuwag Ta Kay
synopsis: Magbuwag Ta Kay tells of college sweethearts Roy and Kay who plan to break up like adults, without the drama, when Kay’s family arranged her entry to Canada. They still have a month left to make great memories together and give their romance the ending it deserves. But you know what Google says about best-laid plans, often they get awkward despite their best intentions.

title: Dendam Orang Mati
synopsis: Kisah ini bermula apabila Lena tersedar dari koma selama dua tahun dan hilang ingatan akibat kemalangan. Keadaan bertambah runsing apabila suaminya Shahrul, memperkenalkan Lena kepada isteri barunya, Min di flat lamanya di tingkat 4 yang kini menjadi tingkat 3A. Tidak lama kemudian, pelbagai kejadian aneh dan menyeramkan mula berlaku di flat tersebut dan Lena yang masih keliru dengan kehidupan barunya mula merasai tekanan akibat pengabaian oleh suaminya yang berbelah bagi antara isteri mudanya dan Lena.

title: My Generation
synopsis: An ordinary school holiday eventually leads four high school students to the events and adventures that end up becoming very meaningful lessons in their lives.

title: House Of Good & Evil
synopsis: After a family tragedy in the chaotic city, Chris and Maggie Conley, in a last-ditch effort to save their dying marriage, purchase an isolated home in the deepest woods, to which they quickly discover evil has a key.

title: The Time Being
synopsis: A young artist (Wes Bentley: The Hunger Games, American Beauty) accepts a series of mysterious assignments from a reclusive millionaire (Frank Langella: Frost/Nixon) hiding a lifetime of family secrets.

title: American Beach House
synopsis: Three young men and three young women from around the world win a contest and get an all-expenses-paid trip to a beach house in Malibu. When they arrive, they find out they have to share the space.

title: Lamaran
synopsis: Tiar Siregar, pengacara muda ambisius, karirnya meroket saat ia berhasil membela Arif Rupawan, bos mafia yang terlibat kasus korupsi. Popularitasnya menjadikan Tiar sasaran ancaman pembunuhan. Khawatir Tiar membocorkan semua kebusukannya, Arif memata-matainya dengan cara menyewa Aan, resepsionis polos di kantor Tiar, untuk menjadi pacar bohongan Tiar. Tak disangka, Aan berhasil mengambil hati Tiar dengan keluguannya. Masalah muncul saat keluarga Tiar yang berasal dari Batak dan keluarga Aan yang berasal dari Sunda menentang hubungan ini. Akankah hubungan ini lanjut atau terhenti sampai di acara lamaran?

title: LSS (Last Song Syndrome)
synopsis: SARA and ZACK, an aspiring musician and a yearning soon find themselves in a series  of almost-but-not-quite romantic encounters as they follow an uprising indie-folk band.Two struggling dreamers in their 20s discover what it means to grow up as they experience the joy and pain of love and loss accompanied by the music of Ben & Ben.

title: Death Of A Ghost Hunter
synopsis: Based on true events, renowned ghost hunter Carter Simms is paid to conduct a paranormal investigation of a suspected haunted house. Along with a cameraman, a reporter, and a spiritual advocate, she embarks on a three night journey into terror.

title: The Lady From 406
synopsis: A lady who lives in room 406 has gone insane from the cigarette smoke of down stairs. She goes to room 306 and complains about it. The man who lives there, however, says something odd. One of Asian top stars, LEE YOUNG-AE’s first starring movie after <LADY VENGEANCE>, directed by PARK CHAN-WOOK and the winner at VENICE. The director, LEE KYOUNG-MI is famous for her brave female characters who are not permitted in conservative Korean society.

title: Borneo's Pygmy Elephants
synopsis: The exotic Southeast Asian island of Borneo is home to the Pygmy Elephant; field researcher Englebert Dausip is sent on a mission through the ancient rainforests and dangerous swamps of the island to locate, track, and study these elusive elephants.

title: Love In Bora Bora
synopsis: Valentine is secretly in love with Jerome, her best friend and colleague. She plans to confess on a work trip but this is foiled when Celeste, Jerome’s girlfriend, tags along. However, as the days go by, she realises she might’ve been wrong all along.

title: Laundry Show
synopsis: Uki quits his office job to start a laundry business. The beginning of his business leads him to deal with the comical and humorous personalities of his own employees. But the main challenge comes from his competition with Agustina, a girl who also owns a laundry business right across his laundry place. Now he has to choose between his business and love.

I was adopted at the age of one. In terms of treatment, I think my parents fared as well as any parent to a child. They never once made me feel like I was different from anybody else. 

I’ve had one too many breakdowns of hyperventilation because I was just overthinking about how unworthy I was in this family and how I do not deserve everything that I have. I really am amazed at how unconditional someone’s love can be for a stranger.
title: Adopted At The Age Of One | No Different From A Biological Child

description: See how Mahershala Ali two-time Oscar winner was turned into an old man for season 3 of “True Detective.” We take a look behind the scenes with Mike Marino the Emmy-nominated makeup designer who transformed Ali and his co-star Stephen Dorff. The artist explains how he used prosthetics and makeup to add decades to the actors’ faces.The newest season of “True Detective” finds Mahershala Ali playing the same character — Detective Wayne Hayes — at three different ages. His performance is incredibly believable and was made possible by the realistic aging FX which turned him into a convincing 75-year old man.  We visited Marino at his studio Prosthetics Renaissance — also known as ProRen FX. They’ve worked on a long list of Hollywood films including “Black Swan” “Wolf of Wall Street” and “Birdman.” ProRen is also the team behind Heidi Klum’s famous Halloween costumes.
title: INSIDER - How Mahershala Ali was turned into an old man for 'True Detective'
